%3A1710315807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F13%2Ffull%2F1710314044-1962.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-economy-has-parallels-to-2000s-where-growth-averaged-over-8-124031300334_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20economists%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%20also%20said%20the%20economy%20appears%20to%20have%20room%20for%20even%20further%20expansion%2C%20given%20the%20path%20for%20additional%20capital%20expenditure%20-%20especially%20from%20private%20businesses%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-economy-has-parallels-to-2000s-where-growth-averaged-over-8-124031300334_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-economy-has-parallels-to-2000s-where-growth-averaged-over-8-124031300334_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-s-economy-has-parallels-to-2000s-where-growth-averaged-over-8-124031300334_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20To%20Hear%20Petition%20On%20Poll%20Officers'%20Appointments%20On%20Friday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20accepted%20the%20request%20for%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20on%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20decision%20to%20exclude%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20from%20the%20panel%20that%20selects%20election%20commissioners.%20Justice%20Sanjeev%20Khanna%20told%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20petitioner%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20that%20they%20have%20got%20a%20message%20from%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20and%20the%20matter%20will%20be%20listed%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20poll%20body%20has%20two%20vacancies%20in%20its%20top%20panel.%20Election%20Commissioner%20Arun%20Goel%20resigned%20last%20week%20and%20his%20colleague%20on%20the%20top%20panel%2C%20Anup%20Chandra%20Pandey%2C%20retired%20last%20month.%20This%20leaves%20only%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20on%20the%20top%20panel%2C%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20the%20biggest%20event%20for%20the%20poll%20body%20-%20is%20weeks%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20current%20procedure%20to%20appoint%20election%20commissioners%2C%20a%20search%20committee%20led%20by%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20will%20prepare%20two%20panels%20of%20five%20names%20each%20for%20the%20two%20posts.%20Later%2C%20a%20selection%20committee%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20comprising%20a%20Union%20Minister%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20will%20name%20two%20persons%20for%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selection%20committee%20is%20likely%20to%20meet%20today%20or%20tomorrow%2C%20and%20government%20sources%20have%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20both%20vacant%20posts%20may%20be%20filled%20by%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ADR's%20petition%20puts%20the%20spotlight%20on%20the%20rules%20for%20appointment%20of%20Election%20Commissioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20Constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20ruled%20that%20the%20top%20poll%20officials%20must%20be%20appointed%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20a%20committee%20comprising%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20later%2C%20the%20Centre%20brought%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(Appointment%2C%20Conditions%20of%20Service%20and%20Term%20of%20Office)%20Bill%2C%202023.%20This%20legislation%2C%20which%20cleared%20the%20Parliament%2C%20dropped%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20from%20the%20selection%20panel.%20Instead%2C%20a%20Union%20Minister%20was%20put%20on%20it.%20This%20gave%20the%20Executive%20more%20heft%20on%20the%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ADR's%20petition%20challenges%20this%20move.%20Congress%20leader%20Jaya%20Thakur%20has%20also%20challenged%20the%20law%20in%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20refused%20to%20pause%20appointments%20under%20the%20new%20law%20last%20month.%20But%20the%20matter%20has%20gathered%20steam%20after%20the%20resignation%20of%20Mr%20Goel.%20The%20Centre%20has%20drawn%20fire%20from%20the%20Opposition%2C%20which%20has%20alleged%20a%20%26quot%3Bsystemic%20decimation%26quot%3B%20of%20government%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2013%2C%20the%20court%20had%20refused%20to%20pause%20appointments%2C%20but%20sought%20the%20Centre's%20reply%20to%20the%20petition%20challenging%20the%20new%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710315720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fe8bgk2vo_supreme-court-getty_625x300_31_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-to-take-up-on-friday-petition-challenging-the-appointment-procedure-of-election-commissioners-5229217%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20accepted%20the%20request%20for%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20on%20a%20petition%20challenging%20the%20decision%20to%20exclude%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20from%20the%20panel%20that%20selects%20election%20commissioners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-to-take-up-on-friday-petition-challenging-the-appointment-procedure-of-election-commissioners-5229217%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-to-take-up-on-