t%20the%20city's%20Rameshwaram%20Cafe%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShabir%20was%20arrested%20this%20morning%20in%20Ballary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20said%20Shabir%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20an%20accomplice%20of%20the%20prime%20suspect%20who%20was%20seen%20leaving%20a%20bag%20at%20the%20cafe%20on%20security%20camera%20footage%20just%20before%20the%20blast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20anti-terror%20agency%2C%20which%20took%20over%20the%20case%20on%20March%203%2C%20has%20sought%20the%20public's%20assistance%20in%20identifying%20the%20prime%20suspect%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20planted%20an%20Improvised%20Explosive%20Device%20(IED)%20in%20the%20popular%20Bengaluru%20eatery%20on%20March%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20footage%20from%20the%20same%20day%20at%20around%209%20pm%2C%20the%20suspect%20is%20observed%20roaming%20inside%20a%20bus%20station.%20Before%20that%2C%20he%20was%20seen%20boarding%20a%20bus%20approximately%20an%20hour%20after%20the%20blast%20occurred%20at%20the%20cafe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20probe%20team%2C%20the%20suspect%20changed%20his%20clothes%20after%20the%20incident%20and%20travelled%20by%20bus%20to%20different%20locations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rameshwaram%20Cafe%20resumed%20operations%20last%20week%20with%20enhanced%20security%20measures.%20Metal%20detectors%20have%20been%20installed%20at%20the%20entrance%2C%20and%20customers%20are%20subjected%20to%20screening%20using%20handheld%20detectors%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20patrons%20and%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20owner%2C%20Divya%20Raghavendra%20Rao%2C%20said%20that%20the%20suspect%20was%20seen%20having%20rava%20idli%20before%20leaving%20his%20bag%20in%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mobile%20phone%20was%20not%20with%20me%20when%20the%20blast%20took%20place%20and%20when%20I%20picked%20it%20up%2C%20there%20were%20too%20many%20missed%20calls.%20When%20I%20called%20back%20my%20team%2C%20they%20told%20me%20that%20there%20was%20a%20blast%20in%20the%20restaurant%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710315480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F7vhgn4lg_rameshwaram-cafe_625x300_04_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Frameshwaram-cafe-bengaluru-blast-key-suspect-in-bengalurus-rameshwaram-cafe-blast-arrested-5229586%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20has%20a%20man%20wanted%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20blast%20that%20left%20nine%20people%20injured%20at%20the%20city's%20Rameshwaram%20Cafe%20earlier%20this%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Frameshwaram-cafe-bengaluru-blast-key-suspect-in-bengalurus-rameshwaram-cafe-blast-arrested-5229586%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Frameshwaram-cafe-bengaluru-blast-key-suspect-in-bengalurus-rameshwaram-cafe-blast-arrested-5229586%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Frameshwaram-cafe-bengaluru-blast-key-suspect-in-bengalurus-rameshwaram-cafe-blast-arrested-5229586%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SKM%20Calls%20for%20Mahapanchayat%20in%20Delhi%20on%20March%2014%2C%20Denounces%20Modi%20Government's%20'Repression'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16201852%2FGGche4VbgAAMUxd.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20a%20statement%20from%20Ashok%20Dhawale%2C%20president%20of%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Sabha%2C%20on%20the%20ongoing%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20and%20upcoming%20Mahapanchayat%20in%20Delhi%2C%20among%20other%20issues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20one%20month%20has%20seen%20a%20strong%20resurgence%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20has%20also%20seen%20an%20equally%20strong%20resurgence%20of%20the%20BJP-RSS%20government%E2%80%99s%20brutal%20repression%20against%20farmers%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20two%20farmer%20martyrs%20so%20far%2C%20and%20many%20more%20seriously%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERepression%20condemned%20nationwide%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20martyrs%20is%2079-year-old%20Gian%20Singh%2C%20who%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20on%20February%2016%2C%20while%20protesting%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border%3B%20the%20other%20is%2021-year-old%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20the%20trigger-happy%20police%20of%20the%20BJP%20Haryana%20government%20on%20February%2021%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20border.%20Both%20these%20borders%20separate%20Punjab%20from%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20killings%20were%20preceded%20by%20the%20shocking%20act%20on%20February%2013%20of%20throwing%20tear%20gas%20shells%20on%20farmers%20from%20drones%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20borders%2C%20firing%20pellets%20and%20rubber%20bullets%2C%20unleashing%20lathi%20charges%2C%20making%20arbitrary%20arrests%2C%20and%20erecting%20huge%20iron%20spikes%2C%20barbed%20wire%2C%20and%20concrete%20barricades%20on%20the%20highways%2C%20just%20to%20prevent%20the%20farmers%20from%20marching%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%2C%20the%20Central%20Trade%20Unions%20(CTU)%2C%20and%20several%20Left%20and%20secular%20political%20parties%20denounced%20the%20BJP-RSS%20government%20for%20its%20savage%20repression.%20The%20SKM%20and%20CTU%20condemned%20the%20February%2013%20repression%20of%20farmers%20during%20the%20nationwide%20rural%20Bharat%20Bandh%20and%20industrial%20strike%20on%20February%2016%20for%20their%20burning%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20and%20CTU%20denounced%20the%20cold-blooded%20murder%20by%20the%20Haryana%20police%20of%20the%20young%20farmer%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%20through%20nationwide%20protests%20on%20February%2023.%20In%20this%20connection%2C%20the%20SKM%20also%20demanded%20the%20resignation%20of%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20and%20Haryana%20home%20minister%20Anil%20Vij.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECynical%20immorality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20all%20this%20came%20the%20shocking%20and%20shameless%20decision%20of%20the%20BJP%20on%20March%203%20to%20give%20the%20ticket%20for%20contesting%20the%20coming%20parliament%20elections%20to%20the%20notorious%20butcher%20of%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni.%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%20is%20today%20still%20the%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%2C%20more%20than%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20after%20he%20and%20his%20son%20crushed%20and%20killed%20four%20farmers%20and%20a%20journalist%20under%20their%20cars%20and%20severely%20injured%20many%20others%20on%20October%203%2C%202021%2C%20when%20the%20SKM-led%20nationwide%20farmers%E2%80%99%20struggle%20against%20the%20three%20black%20Farm%20Laws%20was%20still%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20thing%20would%20be%20unheard%20of%20in%20any%20civilised%20democracy%2C%20in%20which%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20place%20would%20surely%20have%20been%20in%20jail%2C%20and%20certainly%20not%20in%20Parliament%20or%20the%20Cabinet.%20It%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20the%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Boris%20Johnson%2C%20incidentally%20a%20Tory%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20resign%20from%20his%20high%20post%20because%20he%20was%20hosting%20drunken%20parties%20in%20his%20official%20residence%2010%20Downing%20Street%20in%20London%20when%20the%20nation%20was%20reeling%20under%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%20In%20stark%20contrast%2C%20by%20again%20giving%20the%20butcher%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%20a%20ticket%20to%20Parliament%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20BJP-RSS%20top%20brass%20have%20not%20only%20displayed%20their%20utterly%20cynical%20immorality%2C%20but%20they%20have%20also%20insulted%20the%20entire%20farmer%20community%20of%20India%20and%20rubbed%20salt%20into%20their%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697315%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20photo%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%20Credit%3A%20Photo%3A%20Special%20Arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESKM-CTU%20struggle%20calls%20get%20enthusiastic%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20SKM%20National%20Coordination%20Committee%20and%20the%20General%20Body%20which%20met%20at%20Chandigarh%20on%20February%2022%20took%20a%20number%20of%20important%20decisions.%20It%20briefly%20reviewed%20the%20massive%20success%20of%20the%20January%2026%20Nationwide%20Tractor%20Parades%20and%20the%20February%2016%20Rural%20Bharat%20Bandh%20and%20Industrial%20Strike.%20Both%20these%20SKM-CTU%20actions%2C%20the%20Chalo%20Delhi%20call%20by%20other%20organisations%20(we%20are%20at%20the%20moment%20refraining%20from%20commenting%20on%20these%20organisations%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20forging%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unity)%20and%20the%20repression%20by%20the%20government%2C%20served%20two%20vital%20purposes.%20One%2C%20they%20brought%20home%20to%20the%20entire%20country%20that%20the%20struggle%20of%20farmers%20and%20workers%20for%20their%20rights%20was%20far%20from%20over%20and%20would%20be%20intensified.%20Two%2C%20all%20these%20struggles%20succeeded%20in%20partly%20neutralising%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20January%2022%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%20spectacle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20decision%20of%20the%20Chandigarh%20SKM%20meeting%20was%20to%20organise%20a%20massive%20Mahapanchayat%20at%20the%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20on%20March%2014.%20The%20CTU%20declared%20that%20it%20would%20also%20mobilise%20for%20this%20Mahapanchayat%20in%20solidarity.%20Hectic%20preparations%20are%20now%20going%20on%20to%20make%20the%20March%2014%20programme%20a%20great%20success%2C%20especially%20to%20ensure%20mass%20mobilisation%20from%20the%20North%20Indian%20states%20like%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20There%20will%20be%20representative%20mobilisation%20from%20the%20other%20states.%20It%20will%20have%20to%20be%20seen%20what%20the%20response%20of%20the%20authoritarian%20Modi%20regime%20will%20be%2C%20but%20the%20SKM%20has%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20Mahapanchayat%2C%20come%20what%20may.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20major%20decisions%20taken%20in%20the%20February%2022%20SKM%20Chandigarh%20meeting%20were%3A%20Nationwide%20Black%20Day%20protests%20denouncing%20the%20police%20murder%20of%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%3B%20and%20demonstrations%20all%20over%20the%20country%20on%20February%2026%2C%20the%20day%20that%20the%20Ministerial%20Summit%20of%20the%20WTO%20began%20at%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20to%20warn%20against%20any%20likely%20surrender%20by%20India%20to%20WTO%20diktats%20to%20dilute%20the%20demands%20for%20a%20remunerative%20MSP%20and%20a%20strong%20and%20universal%20PDS.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20participated%20in%20both%20these%20protest%20actions%20throughout%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20Chandigarh%20General%20Body%20decided%20to%20form%20a%20six-member%20committee%20to%20hold%20consultations%20with%20all%20former%20SKM%20members%20to%20launch%20a%20united%20action%20plan%20for%20achieving%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands%20and%20develop%20issue-based%20unity%20and%20to%20unite%20all%20Kisan%20organisations%20which%20were%20part%20of%20the%20SKM.%20The%20members%20include%20Hannan%20Mollah%2C%20Joginder%20Singh%20Ugrahan%2C%20Balbeer%20Singh%20Rajewal%2C%20Yudhvir%20Singh%2C%20Darshan%20Pal%20and%20Raminder%20Patiala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20demands%20of%20the%20SKM-CTU%20joint%20struggle%2C%20adopted%20in%20the%20National%20Convention%20of%20Workers%20and%20Farmers%20at%20the%20Talkatora%20Stadium%20in%20Delhi%20on%20August%2024%2C%202023%20are%20as%20follows%3A%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20%40C2%2B50%25%20for%20all%20crops%20with%20guaranteed%20procurement%2C%20Reduction%20by%20half%20of%20all%20input%20costs%20with%20restoration%20of%20fertilizer%20subsidy%2C%20Complete%20loan%20waiver%20to%20small%20and%20middle%20farm%20households%20and%20agricultural%20workers%20to%20ensure%20their%20freedom%20from%20indebtedness%2C%20Radical%20strengthening%20and%20expansion%20of%20the%20Public%20Distribution%20System%20(PDS)%2C%20Comprehensive%20pro-farmer%20crop%20insurance%20scheme%20to%20combat%20natural%20calamities%2C%20No%20hike%20in%20electricity%20tariff%2C%20no%20to%20prepaid%20metres%2C%20300%20units%20free%20electricity%20to%20all%20rural%20households%20and%20shops%2C%20Minimum%20wage%20of%20Rs%2026%2C000%20per%20month%20for%20workers%2C%20Repeal%20of%20the%20four%20Labour%20Codes%2C%20No%20privatisation%20of%20PSUs%20including%20Railway%2C%20Defence%2C%20Electricity%2C%20Coal%2C%20Oil%2C%20Steel%2C%20Telecom%2C%20Posts%2C%20Transport%2C%20Airports%2C%20Port%20%26amp%3B%20Dock%2C%20Banks%2C%20Insurance%2C%20Education%20and%20Health%2C%20Employment%20as%20a%20Fundamental%20Right%2C%20No%20Contractualisation%20of%20jobs%2C%20Scrapping%20of%20Fixed%20Term%20Employment%2C%20Strengthen%20MGNREGS%20with%20200%20days%20work%20per%20person%20per%20year%20and%20Rs%20600%20as%20daily%20wage%2C%20Restore%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%2C%20Pension%20and%20social%20security%20to%20all%20in%20formal%20and%20informal%20economy%2C%20Welfare%20Boards%20for%20all%20categories%20of%20unorganised%20workers%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Construction%20Workers%20Welfare%20Board%2C%20Implementation%20of%20the%20LARR%20Act%202013%20(Right%20to%20Fair%20Compensation%20and%20Transparency%20in%20Land%20Acquisition%2C%20Rehabilitation%20and%20Resettlement%20Act%2C%202013)%2C%20Implementation%20of%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%2C%20dismissal%20of%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%20and%20registration%20of%20murder%20case%20against%20him%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20also%20reiterated%20that%20it%20will%20carry%20forward%20the%20struggle%20against%20communalism%2C%20casteism%20and%20authoritarianism%20to%20save%20the%20Basic%20Principles%20of%20Democracy%2C%20Secularism%2C%20Federalism%2C%20and%20Socialism%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHypocrisy%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20exposed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20February%2010%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20announced%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20highest%20civilian%20award%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20would%20be%20conferred%20on%20Choudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20M.S.%20Swaminathan.%20The%20AIKS%20exposed%20the%20Modi%20regime%20through%20the%20following%20press%20release%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Sabha%20(AIKS)%20is%20of%20the%20clear%20opinion%20that%20the%20BJP%20Central%20Government%20headed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20deciding%20to%20confer%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20Award%20on%20Choudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20M%20S%20Swaminathan%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20is%20the%20height%20of%20hypocrisy.%20By%20this%20step%2C%20the%20Modi%20regime%20is%20trying%20to%20hide%20its%20extreme%20anti-farmer%2C%20anti-agriculture%2C%20and%20pro-corporate%20policies%20of%20the%20last%20ten%20years.%20But%20farmers%20will%20see%20through%20its%20game%2C%20and%20it%20will%20never%20succeed%20in%20hoodwinking%20the%20rural%20populace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20it%20must%20be%20underlined%20that%20during%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%20more%20than%20750%20farmers%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20were%20martyred%20during%20the%20year-long%20iconic%20and%20victorious%20nationwide%20farmers%E2%80%99%20struggle%20against%20the%20three%20hated%20Farm%20Laws%20in%202020-21.%20Many%20families%20of%20these%20farmer%20martyrs%20have%20still%20got%20no%20compensation%20whatsoever%2C%20despite%20written%20assurances%20by%20the%20central%20government.%20The%20Modi%20regime%20is%20also%20the%20only%20government%20in%20independent%20India%20which%20has%20the%20ignominy%20of%20one%20of%20its%20own%20Union%20Ministers%20of%20State%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%20being%20directly%20responsible%20for%20the%20crushing%20to%20death%20of%20four%20farmers%20and%20one%20journalist%20under%20cars%20directed%20by%20him%20at%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20is%20the%20native%20state%20of%20Choudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20a%20renowned%20anti-feudal%20farmer%20leader%20himself.%20What%20is%20worse%2C%20this%20Minister%2C%20instead%20of%20being%20in%20jail%20for%20murder%2C%20still%20retains%20his%20post%20in%20the%20Modi%20Cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20the%20information%20of%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20which%20is%20directly%20under%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20over%20one%20lakh%20farmers%20and%20agricultural%20workers%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20commit%20suicide%20due%20to%20indebtedness%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20of%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government%20alone.%20The%20main%20reason%20for%20this%20terrible%20human%20tragedy%20is%20the%20outright%20refusal%20of%20this%20government%20to%20implement%20the%20most%20seminal%20recommendation%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20on%20Farmers%20(NCF)%2C%20headed%20by%20Dr%20M%20S%20Swaminathan%2C%20of%20giving%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20at%20one%20and%20a%20half%20times%20the%20comprehensive%20cost%20of%20production%20(C2%20%2B%2050%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20Election%20Manifesto%20of%202014%20had%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20will%20enhance%20the%20profitability%20in%20agriculture%2C%20by%20ensuring%20a%20minimum%20of%2050%25%20net%20profit%2C%20cheaper%20agriculture%20inputs%20and%20credit%E2%80%9D.%20The%20same%20assurance%20was%20given%20by%20Modi%20in%20over%20400%20election%20speeches%20during%20the%20campaign.%20But%20what%20did%20the%20government%20actually%20do%20after%20coming%20to%20power%3F%20On%20February%2015%2C%202015%20it%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20increase%20the%20MSP%20for%20food%20grains%20and%20other%20farm%20produce%20to%20input%20cost%20plus%2050%25%20as%20it%20would%20%E2%80%9Cdistort%20the%20market%E2%80%9D.%20Ever%20since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20consistently%20refused%20to%20honour%20any%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20other%20assurance%20that%20was%20given%20by%20Modi%20in%20his%202014%20election%20speeches%20was%20that%20of%20a%20loan%20waiver%20to%20the%20peasantry.%20But%20not%20a%20single%20rupee%20of%20peasants%E2%80%99%20loans%20has%20been%20waived%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20by%20the%20Modi-led%20central%20government.%20The%20Modi%20regime%2C%20while%20stubbornly%20refusing%20a%20peasant%20loan%20waiver%2C%20has%20written%20off%20loans%20worth%20over%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20crores%20that%20had%20been%20taken%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20its%20crony%20corporates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CModi%E2%80%99s%20talk%20of%20doubling%20farmers%E2%80%99%20incomes%20in%20six%20years%20has%20also%20been%20exposed%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98jumla%E2%80%99%20that%20it%20was%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20In%20fact%2C%20as%20the%20latest%20Union%20Budget%20has%20proved%2C%20there%20have%20been%20huge%20cuts%20in%20outlay%20on%20agriculture%20and%20allied%20sectors%2C%20including%20on%20food%20subsidy%2C%20fertiliser%20subsidy%2C%20irrigation%2C%20and%20also%20for%20MNREGA.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20recently%20revealed%20that%20the%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Welfare%20Ministry%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%20shamelessly%20returned%20an%20amount%20of%20over%20Rs%20one%20lakh%20crore%20that%20was%20earmarked%20for%20agriculture%20in%20the%20last%20five%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20thrust%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20has%20been%20to%20fatten%20its%20crony%20corporates%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20peasants%20and%20workers%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20country%20itself.%20This%20was%20seen%20in%20its%20attempt%20to%20steamroller%20the%20three%20Farm%20Laws%2C%20and%20earlier%20the%20reactionary%20amendments%20to%20the%20LARR%202013.%20Both%20these%20attempts%20were%20defeated%20by%20united%20farmers%E2%80%99%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChoudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20M%20S%20Swaminathan%20in%20their%20entire%20life%2C%20thought%2C%20and%20work%2C%20were%20diametrically%20opposed%20to%20this%20entire%20trajectory%20of%20rural%20development%20that%20the%20Modi%20regime%20has%20been%20pushing%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20its%20corporate%20masters%2C%20both%20domestic%20and%20foreign.%20This%20trajectory%20has%20already%20led%20to%20the%20ruin%20of%20Indian%20agriculture%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20peasantry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20peasantry%20of%20India%20will%20surely%20see%20through%20this%20new%20hypocrisy%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20and%20will%20show%20its%20anger%20by%20defeating%20this%20regime%20in%20the%20coming%20elections.%20Its%20determination%20will%20soon%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20great%20success%20of%20the%20Rural%20Bharat%20Bandh%20and%20Industrial%20Strike%20called%20by%20the%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20and%20Central%20Trade%20Unions%20(CTUs)%20on%2016%20February%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710315440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16201852%2FGGche4VbgAAMUxd.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fskm-calls-for-mahapanchayat-in-delhi-on-march-14-denounces-modi-governments-repression%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20massive%20Mahapanchayat%20at%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20in%20Delhi%20would%20witness%20the%20participation%20of%20farmers%20from%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20among%20other%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fskm-calls-for-mahapanchayat-in-delhi-on-march-14-denounces-modi-governments-repression%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B22%2C217%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Bought%20From%202019-24%2C%20Of%20Which%2022%2C030%20Redeemed%26quot%3B%3A%20SBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20a%20rap%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20today%2C%20informing%20that%20it%20had%20submitted%20data%20on%20the%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(EC).%C2%A0The%20SBI%20has%20said%20in%20its%20compliance%20affidavit%20that%20it%20has%20submitted%20the%20data%20to%20the%20poll%20body%20in%20a%20pen%20drive.%20The%20data%2C%20it%20has%20said%2C%20is%20on%20two%20PDF%20files%20that%20are%20password-protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20also%20said%20in%20its%20affidavit%20that%20a%20total%20of%2022%2C217%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20issued%20between%20April%202019%20and%20February%2015%2C%202024%2C%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20junked%20the%20scheme.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%20political%20parties%20redeemed%2022%2C030%20bonds.%20The%20remaining%20187%2C%20the%20bank%20said%2C%20were%20redeemed%20and%20the%20money%20deposited%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20national%20relief%20fund%2C%20according%20to%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20now-scrapped%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20donors%20could%20purchase%20bonds%20to%20donate%20to%20parties%20of%20their%20choice.%20But%20the%20parties%20had%20to%20redeem%20the%20bonds%20within%2015%20days%2C%20failing%20which%20the%20amount%20would%20go%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20relief%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20landmark%20February%2015%20verdict%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20held%20that%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20was%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bviolates%20the%20right%20to%20information%20of%20citizens%2C%20about%20possible%20quid%20pro%20quo%26quot%3B%20between%20donors%20and%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESBI%20had%20been%20ordered%20to%20stop%20issuing%20the%20bonds%20immediately%20and%20submit%20the%20details%20of%20the%20donations%20to%20the%20EC%2C%20which%20would%20make%20them%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20set%20a%20deadline%20of%20March%206%20for%20SBI%20to%20submit%20the%20data%2C%20and%20the%20EC%20had%20been%20asked%20to%20make%20it%20public%20by%20March%2013.%20But%20the%20bank%20requested%20the%20court%20for%20an%20extension%20till%20June%2030.%20This%20was%20challenged%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20which%20was%20among%20the%20petitioners%20who%20had%20opposed%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20court%20turned%20down%20the%20SBI's%20request%20and%20said%20it%20must%20share%20the%20details%20by%20Tuesday.%20The%20EC%20has%20now%20been%20asked%20to%20upload%20the%20data%20on%20its%20website%20by%205%20pm%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20SBI%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Harish%20Salve%20had%20said%20the%20bank%20had%20followed%20an%20SOP%20to%20store%20information%20about%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20outside%20the%20core%20banking%20system.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20full%20details%20on%20who%20purchased%20the%20bond%20and%20I%20have%20full%20details%20from%20where%20the%20money%20came%20from%20and%20which%20political%20party%20tendered%20how%20much.%20I%20have%20to%20also%20now%20put%20the%20name%20of%20purchasers.%20The%20names%20have%20to%20be%20collated%2C%20crosschecked%20with%20the%20bond%20numbers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20the%20court%20replied%20that%20it%20has%20not%20asked%20the%20bank%20to%20match%20the%20donors%20with%20the%20amount%20received%20by%20political%20parties.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20asked%20you%20to%20do%20the%20matching%20exercise.%20So%20to%20seek%20time%20saying%20that%20a%20matching%20exercise%20is%20to%20be%20done%20is%20not%20warranted%2C%20we%20have%20not%20directed%20you%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710315420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F4l1gu19o_sbi-_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F22-217-electoral-bonds-bought-from-2019-24-of-which-22-030-redeemed-sbi-5229779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20days%20after%20a%20rap%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20today%2C%20informing%20that%20it%20had%20submitted%20data%20on%20the%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(EC).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F22-217-electoral-bonds-bought-from-2019-24-of-which-22-030-redeemed-sbi-5229779%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F22-217-electoral-bonds-bought-from-2019-24-of-which-22-030-redeemed-sbi-5229779%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F22-217-electoral-bonds-bought-from-2019-24-of-which-22-030-redeemed-sbi-5229779%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electoral%20bonds%20case%3A%20SBI%20submits%20compliance%20affidavit%20in%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710315409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F23%2Ffull%2F1700736920-4358.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-case-sbi-submits-compliance-affidavit-in-supreme-court-124031300351_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20divulged%20details%20about%20the%20purchase%20and%20redeeming%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20between%20April%201%2C%202019%20to%20February%2015%2C%202024%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-case-sbi-submits-compliance-affidavit-in-supreme-court-124031300351_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-case-sbi-submits-compliance-affidavit-in-supreme-court-124031300351_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-case-sbi-submits-compliance-affidavit-in-supreme-court-124031300351_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShameful%20Gender%20Bias%26quot%3B%3A%20Kiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20Slams%20'Pink%20Tax'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBiocon%20chief%20Kiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20has%20reacted%20strongly%20against%20'Pink%20Tax'%2C%20a%20term%20used%20for%20gender-based%20price%20disparity.%20She%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20X%20that%20showed%20why%20women's%20products%20of%20same%20category%20are%20far%20more%20expensive%20than%20male%20products%20of%20the%20same%20size%20and%20quantity.%20In%20the%20accompanying%20post%2C%20she%20asked%20women%20to%20shun%20such%20products.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fagenda%2F2022%2F07%2Fwhat-is-the-pink-tax-and-how-does-it-hinder-women%2F%5C%22%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%20(WEF)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20gender-based%20price%20disparities%20are%20prevalent%20in%20several%20sectors%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20most%20visible%20is%20personal%20care%20products.%20These%20include%2C%20for%20example%2C%20soaps%2C%20lotions%2C%20razor%20blades%20and%20deodorants%20that%20are%20marketed%20specifically%20to%20either%20women%20or%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPink%20Tax!%20A%20shameful%20gender%20bias%20that%20women%20must%20respond%20to%20by%20shunning%20such%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20said%20in%20her%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPink%20Tax!%20A%20shameful%20gender%20bias%20that%20women%20must%20respond%20to%20by%20shunning%20such%20products!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FU3ZQm2s7W9%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FU3ZQm2s7W9%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%20(%40kiranshaw)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkiranshaw%2Fstatus%2F1767701844758052979%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20was%20shared%20early%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20and%20amassed%201.58%20lakh%20views%20within%20few%20hours.%20Others%20users%20supported%20the%20entrepreneur's%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbsolutely%20agree.%20Question%20is%20how%20should%20we%20get%20around%20it%3F%20%C2%A0It%20seems%20a%20hard%20choice%20between%20buying%20male%20products%20or%20not%20buying%20these%20products%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20one%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20consistently%20point%20out%20the%20higher%20costs%20of%20women's%20products.%20The%20pink%20tax%20is%20prevalent%20in%20various%20places.%20It's%20great%20to%20see%20him%20bringing%20attention%20to%20it%20and%20you%20amplifying%20the%20issue.%20Hopefully%2C%20more%20voices%20will%20join%20in%20and%20push%20for%20the%20elimination%20of%20the%20pink%20tax%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20Pink%20Tax%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pink%20tax%20isn't%20an%20actual%20a%20government%20tax%3B%20it%20refers%20to%20discriminatory%20pricing%20that%20inflates%20the%20cost%20of%20goods%20marketed%20to%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20issue%20got%20attention%20when%20New%20York%20City's%20Department%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%20found%20many%20instances%20of%20gendered%20pricing%20when%20it%20examined%20794%20products%20sold%20in%20the%20city%20for%20consumers%20of%20all%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20researchers%20have%20been%20analysing%20the%20phenomenon%20since%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomic%20Burden%20of%20Pink%20Tax%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20WEF%2C%20the%20discriminatory%20pricing%20has%20put%20an%20economic%20burden%20on%20women%2C%20since%20they%20continue%20to%20earn%20less%20than%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20has%20called%20on%20countries%20worldwide%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20eliminate%20the%20pink%20tax%20to%20ensure%20women%20achieve%20full%20and%20equal%20participation%20in%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%