th%20Test%2C%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20fell%20on%2056%20off%2060%20balls.%20His%20entertaining%20knock%20consisted%20eight%20fours%20and%20one%20six.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20just%20when%20it%20looked%20like%20Sarfaraz%20was%20going%20to%20get%20a%20big%20score%2C%20he%20fell%20on%20the%20first%20ball%20of%20the%20third%20session%20to%20Shoaib%20Bashir.%20Sarfaraz%20was%20caught%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Joe%20Root%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1433-joe-root-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJoe%20Root%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20slips%20as%20his%20late%20cut%20went%20wrong.%20Before%20that%2C%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Devdutt%20Padikkal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110591-devdutt-padikkal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDevdutt%20Padikkal%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20struck%20a%2095-plus%20stand.%20After%20Sarfaraz's%20dismissal%2C%20India%20lost%20wickets%20in%20quick%20succession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20attempt%20by%20Sarfaraz%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ball%20was%20pitched%20up%3B%20it%20wasn't%20short%20enough%20for%20that%20shot.%20Goes%20for%20it%20and%20pays%20the%20price.%20I%20mean%20you%20are%20playing%20the%20first%20ball%20after%20tea.%20Give%20yourself%20a%20little%20sighter.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Don%20Bradman%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40187-donald-george-bradman-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDon%20Bradman%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20to%20me%20'Every%20ball%20that%20I%20face%2C%20even%20if%20I%20am%20on%20200%2C%20I%20think%20I%20am%20on%200.'%20And%20here%20is%20%5BSarfaraz%5D%20is...%20playing%20such%20a%20shot%20first%20ball%20of%20the%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20Gav