overnment%20of%20India%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%26quot%3B.%20India%20has%20trashed%20the%20allegations%2C%20describing%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%26quot%3B.%20Bilateral%20relations%20between%20the%20countries%20have%20since%20nose-dived.%20In%20October%2C%20Canada%20withdrew%2041%20diplomats%2C%20citing%20an%20Indian%20threat%20to%20%26quot%3Bunethically%20revoke%26quot%3B%20their%20diplomatic%20immunity.%C2%A0India%20had%20then%20rejected%20the%C2%A0idea%20that%20it%20had%20violated%20the%20Vienna%20convention%20on%20diplomatic%20relations.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20state%20of%20our%20bilateral%20relations%2C%20the%20much%20higher%20number%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20in%20India%2C%20and%20their%20continued%20interference%20in%20our%20internal%20affairs%20warrant%20a%20parity%20in%20mutual%20diplomatic%20presence%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Ottawa%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20an%20ally%20of%20both%20Canada%20and%20India%2C%20has%20said%20Washington%20DC%20has%20engaged%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20on%20the%20issue.%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20has%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20consulting%20throughout%20very%20closely%20with%20our%20Canadian%20colleagues%20-%20and%20not%20just%20consulting%2C%20coordinating%20with%20them%20-%20on%20this%20issue.%20And%20from%20our%20perspective%2C%20it%20is%20critical%20that%20the%20Canadian%20investigation%20proceed%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20important%20that%20India%20work%20with%20the%20Canadians%20on%20this%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20Canada%20David%20Cohen%20last%20year%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20%26quot%3Bshared%20intelligence%26quot%3B%20among%20partners%20of%20Five%20Eyes%20-%20an%20intelligence%20alliance%20of%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20-%20helped%20lead%20Canada%20to%20make%20the%20statements%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(Trudeau)%20made%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20questions%20on%20whether%20Canada%20had%20shared%20information%20on%20the%20Nijjar%20case%20with%20its%20'Five%20Eyes'%20allies%2C%20Mr%20Peters%20said%20it%20was%20handled%20by%20the%20previous%20New%20Zealand%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2078-year-old%2C%20who%20is%20visiting%20India%2C%20became%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20after%20Centre-Right%20parties%20came%20to%20power%20in%20New%20Zealand%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20here%2C%20it%20was%20handled%20by%20the%20previous%20government.%20But%20look%2C%20sometimes%20when%20you%20are%20hearing%20Five%20Eyes%20information%2C%20you%20are%20hearing%20it%20and%20saying%20nothing%2C%20it's%20coming%20past%20you.%20You%20don't%20know%20the%20value%20or%20the%20quality%20of%20it%2C%20but%20you%20are%20pleased%20to%20have%20it.%20You%20don't%20know%20whether%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20substantial%20material%20value%20or%20nothing.%20But%20the%20very%2C%20very%20critical%20information%20that%20matters...%20This%20was%20mainly%20handled%20by%20the%20previous%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20trained%20lawyer%2C%20I%20look%20okay%2C%20so%20where's%20the%20case%3F%20Where's%20the%20evidence%3F%20Where's%20the%20finding%20right%20here%2C%20right%20now%3F%20Well%2C%20there%20isn't%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20a%20Five%20Eyes%20partner%20has%20questioned%20Canada's%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20India%20trip%2C%20Mr%20Peters%20met%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20and%20also%20visited%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710313260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ff4tuq41g_winston-peters_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%