tions%20and%20in%20the%20field%20of%20strategic%20restraint%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20here%20everything%20is%20rushing%20to%20it%20(nuclear%20confrontation)%2C%20but%20we%20are%20ready%20for%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20triggered%20the%20deepest%20crisis%20in%20Russia's%20relations%20with%20the%20West%20since%20the%201962%20Cuban%20Missile%20Crisis%20and%20Putin%20has%20warned%20several%20times%20that%20the%20West%20risks%20provoking%20a%20nuclear%20war%20if%20it%20sends%20troops%20to%20fight%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20sent%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20troops%20into%20Ukraine%20in%20February%202022%2C%20triggering%20full-scale%20war%20after%20eight%20years%20of%20conflict%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%20between%20Ukrainian%20forces%20on%20one%20side%20and%20pro-Russian%20Ukrainians%20and%20Russian%20proxies%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWestern%20leaders%20have%20promised%20to%20defeat%20Russia%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20after%20two%20years%20of%20war%2C%20Russian%20forces%20control%20a%20little%20under%20one%20fifth%20of%20Ukrainian%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20U.S.%20election%20year%2C%20the%20West%20is%20grappling%20with%20how%20to%20support%20Kyiv%20against%20Russia%20which%20has%20bolstered%20its%20army%20with%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20men%20and%20is%20rearming%20much%20faster%20than%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKyiv%20says%20it%20is%20defending%20itself%20against%20an%20imperial-style%20war%20of%20conquest%20designed%20to%20erase%20its%20national%20identity.%20Russia%20says%20the%20areas%20it%20controls%20in%20Ukraine%20are%20now%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ENUCLEAR%20WAR%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%2C%20Russia's%20ultimate%20decision%20maker%20on%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20reiterated%20that%20the%20use%20of%20nuclear%20weapons%20was%20spelled%20out%20in%20the%20Kremlin's%20nuclear%20doctrine%2C%20its%20policy%20setting%20out%20the%20circumstances%20in%20which%20Russia%20might%20use%20its%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWeapons%20exist%20in%20order%20to%20use%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20our%20own%20principles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20and%20the%20United%20States%20are%20by%20far%20the%20largest%20nuclear%20powers%2C%20controlling%20more%20than%2090%25%20of%20the%20world's%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20said%20Russia%20was%20ready%20for%20serious%20talks%20on%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussia%20is%20ready%20for%20negotiations%20on%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20they%20should%20be%20based%20on%20reality%20-%20and%20not%20on%20cravings%20after%20the%20use%20of%20psychotropic%20drugs%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20reported%20last%20month%20that%20Putin's%20suggestion%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Ukraine%20to%20freeze%20the%20war%20was%20rejected%20by%20the%20United%20States%20after%20contacts%20between%20intermediaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20United%20States%20conducted%20nuclear%20tests%2C%20Russia%20might%20do%20the%20same%2C%20he%20added%20in%20the%20wide-ranging%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20necessary%20...%20we%20still%20need%20to%20think%20about%20it%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20rule%20out%20that%20we%20can%20do%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECNN%20reported%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20administration%20of%20U.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20specifically%20concerned%20in%202022%20that%20Russia%20might%20use%20a%20tactical%20or%20battlefield%20nuclear%20weapon%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECNN%20said%20U.S.%20intelligence%20agencies%20received%20information%20there%20were%20communications%20among%20Russian%20officials%20explicitly%20discussing%20a%20nuclear%20strike%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Putin%20said%20Russia%20had%20never%20faced%20a%20need%20to%20use%20nuclear%20weapons%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20where%20the%20conflict%20has%20raged%20since%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20do%20we%20need%20to%20use%20weapons%20of%20mass%20destruction%3F%20There%20has%20never%20been%20such%20a%20need.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710312240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1lam6j78_putin-reuters_625x300_13_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-warns-us-says-russia-ready-for-nuclear-war-over-ukraine-5228894%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20warned%20the%20West%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Russia%20was%20technically%20ready%20for%20nuclear%20war%20and%20that%20if%20the%20U.S.%20sent%20troops%20to%20Ukraine%20it%20would%20be%20considered%20a%20significant%20escalation%20of%20the%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-warns-us-says-russia-ready-for-nuclear-war-over-ukraine-5228894%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-warns-us-says-russia-ready-for-nuclear-war-over-ukraine-5228894%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-warns-us-says-russia-ready-for-nuclear-war-over-ukraine-5228894%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BInsulted%3F%20Join%20Us%26quot%3B%3A%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20To%20Union%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20has%20again%20asked%20Union%20minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20to%20leave%20the%20BJP%20if%20he%20is%20being%20%26quot%3Binsulted%26quot%3B%2C%20saying%20the%20opposition%20in%20Maharashtra%20would%20ensure%20his%20victory%20in%20the%20upcoming