ng%20Vanke's%20discussions%20with%20banks%20to%20help%20the%20developer%20avert%20a%20default%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-12%2Fchina-vanke-in-debt-swap-talks-with-banks-to-stave-off-default%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20citing%20unnamed%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing's%20intervention%20in%20Vanke%20underscores%20just%20how%20important%20the%20massive%20property%20firm%20is%20to%20China's%20economy.%20Last%20year%2C%20it%20sold%20375.5%20billion%20Chinese%20yuan%2C%20or%20%2452.2%20billion%2C%20worth%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingtiandi.com%2Freal-estate%2Fresearch-policy%2Fcountry-garden-slips-to-6th-among-chinas-top-developers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal%20estate.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Vanke's%20importance%20is%20not%20merely%20about%20the%20number%20of%20apartments%20it%20sells%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20a%20lot%2C%20since%20it%20consistently%20ranked%20as%20one%20of%20China's%20top%20developers%20for%20at%20least%20the%20last%20decade.%20Instead%2C%20it's%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20it's%20a%20huge%2C%20state-backed%20company.%20State-owned%20Shenzhen%20Metro%20holds%20one-third%20stake%20in%20Vanke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20China's%20property%20downturn%2C%20Vanke%20was%20considered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bondsupermart.com%2Fbsm%2Farticle-detail%2Fchina-vanke-is-the-advancing-giant-in-chinese-real-estate-falling-down-RCMS_282041%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20financially%20sound%20developer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20one%20of%20the%20few%20Chinese%20developers%20that%20still%20holds%20investment-grade%20credit%20ratings%20from%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20and%20Fitch.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moodys.com%2Fcredit-ratings%2FChina-Vanke-Co-Ltd-credit-rating-820391194%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoody's%20downgraded%20Vanke%3C%2