oor-test-ex-allys-whip-raises-eyebrows-5229536%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-haryana-floor-test-jjp-dushyant-chautala-ahead-of-bjps-haryana-floor-test-ex-allys-whip-raises-eyebrows-5229536%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-haryana-floor-test-jjp-dushyant-chautala-ahead-of-bjps-haryana-floor-test-ex-allys-whip-raises-eyebrows-5229536%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boeing%20Whistleblower's%20Family%20Blames%20%26quot%3BHostile%20Work%20Environment%26quot%3B%20For%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Boeing%20employee%20John%20Barnett%2C%20who%20questioned%20the%20aircraft%20manufacturer's%20production%20standards%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20US.%20The%2062-year-old%20died%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bself-inflicted%26quot%3B%20gunshot%20wound%20on%20March%209.%20Mr%20Barnett%20was%20in%20Charleston%20for%20legal%20interviews%20and%20was%20scheduled%20for%20additional%20questioning.%20He%20was%20found%20dead%20after%20failing%20to%20appear.%20He%20departed%20from%20Boeing%20in%202017%20due%20to%20health%20reasons%20after%20more%20than%2030%20years%20of%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Barnett's%C2%A0family%20has%20now%20blamed%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bhostile%20work%20environment%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20death%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F03%2F12%2Fus-news%2Ffamily-of-boeing-whistleblower-john-barnett-blames-hostile-work-environment-for-his-death%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20suffering%20from%20PTSD%20and%20anxiety%20attacks%20as%20a%20result%20of%20being%20subjected%20to%20the%20hostile%20work%20environment%20at%20Boeing%20which%20we%20believe%20led%20to%20his%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2062-year-old's%20family%20said%20that%20he%20was%20happily%20working%20for%20the%20jetliner%20giant%20until%202010%20when%20he%20was%20moved%20to%20the%20787%20plant%20in%20Charleston.%20%26quot%3BThings%20greatly%20changed%20for%20him%20when%20he%20learned%20that%20upper%20management%20was%20pressuring%20the%20quality%20inspectors%20and%20managers%20to%20cut%20corners%20and%20to%20not%20follow%20processes%20and%20procedures%20which%20they%20were%20required%20by%20law%20to%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20family%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20alleged%20that%20to%20prevent%20the%20assembly%20line%20from%20slowing%20down%2C%20Boeing%20put%20pressure%20on%20employees%20to%20overlook%20flaws%2C%20and%20those%20who%20resisted%20%26quot%3Bwere%20labelled%20as%20trouble%20makers%2C%20retaliated%20against%2C%20and%20subjected%20to%20a%20hostile%20work%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Barnett%20told%20his%20family%20that%20it%20was%20a%20battle%20for%20him%20to%20get%20the%20management%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing.%20The%20family%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20aircraft%20and%20flying%20public%2C%20and%20had%20identified%20some%20serious%20defects%20that%20he%20felt%20were%20not%20adequately%20addressed.%20He%20said%20that%20Boeing%20had%20a%20culture%20of%20concealment%20and%20was%20putting%20profits%20over%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20job%20he%20once%20loved%20became%20so%20stressful%2C%20Barnett's%20doctor%20grew%20concerned%20for%20his%20health.%20It%20caused%20him%20so%20much%20stress%20that%20his%20doctor%20told%20him%20that%20if%20he%20stayed%2C%20he%20would%20have%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20released%20a%20statement%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20saddened%20by%20Mr.%20Barnett's%20passing%2C%20and%20our%20thoughts%20are%20with%20his%20family%20and%20friends.%26quot%3B%20It%20refrained%20from%20addressing%20the%20points%20raised%20in%20his%20family's%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Barnett%20had%20been%20recently%20giving%20evidence%20in%20a%20whistleblower%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20US%20airplane%20manufacturer%2C%20which%20has%20suffered%20a%20series%20of%20safety%20issues%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20including%20the%20fatal%20Lion%20Air%20and%20Ethiopian%20Airlines%20crashes%20of%20737%20MAX%20planes%20in%202018%20and%202019%20that%20killed%20more%20than%20350%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20John%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bunder-pressure%20workers%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20deliberately%20fitting%20%26quot%3Bsub-standard%20parts%26quot%3B%20to%20Boeing%20aircraft%20on%20the%20production%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Barnett%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20uncovered%20serious%20problems%20with%20oxygen%20systems%2C%20which%20could%20mean%20one%20in%20four%20breathing%20masks%20would%20not%20work%20in%20an%20emergency.%20He%20also%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20workers%20had%20failed%20to%20follow%20procedures%20intended%20to%20track%20components%20through%20the%20factory%2C%20allowing%20defective%20components%20to%20go%20missing.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20had%20alerted%20managers%20about%20the%20concerns%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20take%20any%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710311160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F6kdldnl_john-barnett_625x300_13_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fboeing-whistleblowers-family-blames-hostile-work-environment-for-his-death-5229542%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20family%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20suffering%20from%20PTSD%20and%20anxiety%20attacks%20as%20a%20result%20of%20being%20subjected%20to%20the%20hostile%20work%20environment%20at%20Boeing%20which%20we%20believe%20led%20to%20his%20death.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fb