ely%20due%20to%20a%20family%20medical%20emergency.%20In%20these%20challenging%20times%2C%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20and%20the%20team%20fully%20supports%20Ashwin%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BCCI%20in%20its%20release.%20Reports%20said%20Ashwin's%20mother%20Chitra%20had%20suffered%20a%20medical%20emergency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Ashwin%20has%20revealed%20how%20exactly%20thing%20transpired.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20went%20to%20the%20dressing%20room%20for%20another%20debrief%20and%20then%20back%20to%20our%20rooms.%20Rohit%2C%20me%2C%20and%20others%20were%20just%20discussing%20some%20things%20about%20the%20match%20here%20and%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20when%20I%20realized%20I%20was%20not%20getting%20calls%20from%20my%20parents%20or%20wife.%20I%20thought%20they%20were%20busy%20attending%20calls%20and%20giving%20interviews.%20I%20called%20my%20wife%20around%207%20PM%2C%20asking%20why%20my%20parents%20weren't%20answering%20my%20call.%20Her%20voice%20was%20a%20bit%20shaky.%20She%20asked%20me%20to%20come%20separately%20from%20the%20crowd%20and%20told%20me%20that%20my%20mother%20collapsed%20after%20a%20headache%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgBQNttRczt8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20blanked%20out.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20react%20or%20what%20questions%20to%20ask.%20I%20was%20crying%20but%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20nobody%20was%20watching%20me%20cry.%20It%20is%20unnecessary%20to%20think%20of%20it%20that%20way%2C%20but%20it%20was%20instinctive.%20I%20could%20not%20think.%20I%20was%20crying%20in%20my%20room%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20the%20team%20physio%20checked%20on%20me%20as%20I%20was%20not%20picking%20up%20calls.%20Rahul%20Bhai%20and%20Rohit%20Bhai%20also%20came%20to%20check%20on%20me%2C%20and%20all%20I%20could%20tell%20them%20was%20that%20I%20could%20not%20think%20clearly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20moment%20of%20personal%20shock%2C%20Ashwin%20said%20he%20was%20thinking%20about%20the%20team.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20am%20part%20of%20the%20playing%20XI%2C%20and%20the%20game%20is%20in%20the%20balance.%20If%20I%20leave%2C%20the%20squad%20will%20be%20left%20with%2010%20people%20fighting%20against%20a%20full-strength%20England%20squad%20when%20they%20had%20the%20upper%20hand.%20If%20I%20go%2C%20they%20will%20be%20a%20bowler%20short.%20There%20were%20so%20many%20things%20going%20through%20my%20mind.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20was%20on%20another%20track%20in%20my%20head%2C%20thinking%20about%20the%20last%20time%20I%20spoke%20to%20my%20mother.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20see%20her%20and%20then%20come%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20how%20she%20was%20and%20if%20she%20was%20conscious%2C%20but%20the%20doctor%20apparently%20told%20me%20that%20she%20was%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20be%20seen.%20I%20lost%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20then%20revealed%20how%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20helped%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20searching%20for%20a%20flight%2C%20but%20I%20could%20not%20find%20one.%20The%20Rajkot%20airport%20closes%20at%206%20PM%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20flights%20from%20there%20after%206%20PM.%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20Rohit%20and%20Rahul%20Bhai%20came%20to%20my%20room%2C%20and%20Rohit%20asked%20me%20to%20stop%20thinking.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20go%20to%20my%20family%2C%20and%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20arrange%20a%20charter%20flight%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20big%20thank%20you%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Cheteshwar%20Pujara%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F897-cheteshwar-pujara-playerprofile%5C%22%3ECheteshwar%20Pujara%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20he%20somehow%20found%20some%20flights%20in%20Ahmedabad%20and%20made%20it%20here%20to%20Rajkot%20for%20me%20to%20travel%20in.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20how%20those%20two%20hours%20went%20by%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohit%20did%20something%20else%20-%20he%20asked%20Kamlesh%2C%20our%20physio%2C%20to%20fly%20with%20me%20to%20Chennai%20and%20be%20with%20me.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20the%20two%20physios%20for%20the%20team.%20During%20our%20ride%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20Rohit%20kept%20calling%20and%20asking%20him%20to%20be%20with%20me%20during%20this%20challenging%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710308460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fkbtkdivg_r-ashwin-mother-806_625x300_17_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fmom-collapsed-doctor-said-not-in-position-to-r-ashwin-reveals-how-trauma-struck-during-rajkot-test-5226518%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin's%20mother%20fell%20ill%20during%20India%20vs%20England%203rd%20Test%20and%20the%20star%20cricketer%20had%20to%20rush%20off%20mid-match%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sydney%20Sweeney%E2%80%99s%20Horror%20Film%20%E2%80%98Immaculate%E2%80%99%20Jump%20Scares%20the%20Crap%20Out%20of%20SXSW%20Premiere%20Crowd%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710308014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBUC_6075-e1710307291706.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22origi