'He%20called%20me%20to%20his%20office.%20He%20had%20these%20very%20low%20'70s%2C%20and%20'80s%20couches%2C%20so%20I'm%20essentially%20sitting%20on%20the%20floor%20when%20I%20should%20have%20been%20on%20set.%20And%20he's%20running%20around%20his%20office%20in%20sunglasses%20explaining%20to%20me%20that%20he%20slept%20with%20Ava%20Gardner%20and%20I%20should%20sleep%20with%20Billy%20Baldwin%2C%20because%20if%20I%20slept%20with%20Billy%20Baldwin%2C%20Billy%20Baldwin's%20performance%20would%20get%20better%2C%20and%20we%20needed%20Billy%20to%20get%20better%20in%20the%20movie%20because%20that%20was%20the%20problem%2C''%20the%2066-year-old%20said%20during%20the%20podcast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''And%20if%20I%20could%20sleep%20with%20Billy%20then%20we'd%20have%20chemistry%20on%20screen%2C%20and%20if%20I%20would%20just%20have%20sex%20with%20him%20then%20that%20would%20save%20the%20movie%2C%20and%20the%20real%20problem%20with%20the%20movie%20was%20me%20because%20I%20was%20so%20uptight%2C%20and%20so%20not%20like%20a%20real%20actress%20who%20could%20just%20f**k%20him%20and%20get%20things%20back%20on%20track.%20The%20real%20problem%20was%20I%20was%20such%20a%20tight%20a**e%2C''%20she%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mr%20Baldwin%20hit%20back%20at%20her%20accusations%20in%20a%20lengthy%20post%20on%20X%20and%20threatened%20to%20''write%20a%20book%20and%20tell%20the%20many%2C%20many%20disturbing%2C%20kinky%20and%20unprofessional%20tales%20about%20Sharon.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fsection%3E%5Cn%3Csection%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Not%20sure%20why%20Sharon%20Stone%20keeps%20talking%20about%20me%20all%20these%20years%20later%3F%20Does%20she%20still%20have%20a%20crush%20on%20me%20or%20is%20she%20still%20hurt%20after%20all%20these%20years%20because%20I%20shunned%20her%20advances%3F...%20I%20have%20so%20much%20dirt%20on%20her%20it%20would%20make%20her%20head%20spin%20but%20I've%20kept%20quiet''%2C%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%C2%A0%20He%20also%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20him%20and%20Ms%20Stone%20during%20an%20intimate%20scene%20in%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20tweet%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENot%20sure%20why%20Sharon%20Stone%20keep%20talking%20about%20me%20all%20these%20years%20later%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDoes%20she%20still%20have%20a%20crush%20on%20me%20or%20is%20she%20still%20hurt%20after%20all%20these%20years%20because%20I%20shunned%20her%20advances%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDid%20she%20say%20to%20her%20gal%20pal%20Janice%20Dickinson%20the%20day%20after%20I%20screen%20tested%20and%20ran%20into%20them%20on%20our%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPtgqMC6Sgz%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPtgqMC6Sgz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Billy%20Baldwin%20(%40BillyBaldwin)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBillyBaldwin%2Fstatus%2F1767611327986766089%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Stone%20had%20previously%20written%20about%20the%20incident%20in%20her%202021%20memoir%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Beauty%20of%20Living%20Twice%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20didn't%20name%20either%20the%20producer%20or%20actor%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20book%2C%20she%20shared%20that%20a%20producer%20tried%20to%20pressure%20her%20into%20having%20sex%20with%20her%20co-star%20as%20a%20way%20to%20%E2%80%9Chave%20onscreen%20chemistry%2C%E2%80%9D%20but%20confirmed%20that%20she%20never%20did%20anything.%20Ms%20Stone%20wrote%2C%20''I%20felt%20they%20could%20have%20just%20hired%20a%20co-star%20with%20talent%2C%20someone%2C%20who%20could%20deliver%20a%20scene%20and%20remember%20his%20lines.%20I%20also%20felt%20that%20they%20could%20f%E2%80%94%20him%20themselves%20and%20leave%20me%20out%20of%20it.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Robert%20Evans%20best%20known%20for%20his%20work%20on%20'%3Cem%3ERosemary's%20Baby'%2C%20'Love