was%20hijacked.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20have%20exposed%20a%20potentially%20major%20security%20vulnerability%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-quest-pro%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta's%20virtual%20reality%20headsets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20researchers%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%20said%20figured%20out%20a%20way%20to%20hack%20into%20Meta%20Quest%20headsets%20without%20the%20user%20knowing%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20control%20the%20user's%20VR%20environment%2C%20steal%20information%2C%20and%20even%20manipulate%20interactions%20between%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20called%20the%20strategy%20an%20%26quot%3Binception%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20they%20defined%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20attack%20where%20the%20attacker%20controls%20and%20manipulates%20the%20user's%20interaction%20with%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fextended-reality-fitness-brands-meta-quest-headset-workouts-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVR%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20by%20trapping%20the%20user%20inside%20a%20single%2C%20malicious%20VR%20application%20that%20masquerades%20as%20the%20full%20VR%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20comes%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-is-becoming-metas-ultimate-influencer-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20continues%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-slams-apple-vision-pro-again-meta-quest-vr-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edump%20on%20the%20Apple%20Vision%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20top%20competitor%20in%20the%20space.%20Last%20week%2C%20Zuckerberg%20said%20Apple's%20VR%20headset%20was%20%26quot%3Bworse%20in%20most%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fpdf%2F2403.05721.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20first%20reported%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.technologyreview.com%2F2024%2F03%2F11%2F1089686%2Fhack-vr-headsets-inception%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMIT%20Technology%20Review%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20peer-reviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20hackers%20had%20to%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20same%20WiFi%20network%20as%20the%20Quest%20user%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%20The%20headset%20also%20had%20to%20be%20in%20developer%20mode%2C%20which%20the%20researchers%20said%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-used-metas-virtual-reality-headset-in-office-in-metaverse-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20Quest%3C%2Fa%3E%20users%20keep%20enabled%20in%20order%20to%20get%20third-party%20apps%2C%20adjust%20resolution%2C%20and%20take%20screenshots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%20the%20researchers%20were%20able%20to%20plant%20malware%20onto%20the%20headset%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20install%20a%20phony%20home%20screen%20that%20looked%20identical%20to%20the%20user's%20original%20screen%2C%20but%20that%20could%20be%20controlled%20by%20the%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20duplicate%20home%20screen%20is%20essentially%20a%20simulation%20within%20a%20simulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20user%20thinks%20they%20are%20interacting%20normally%20with%20different%20VR%20applications%2C%20they%20are%20in%20fact%20interacting%20within%20a%20simulated%20world%2C%20where%20everything%20they%20see%20and%20hear%20has%20been%20intercepted%2C%20relayed%2C%20and%20possibly%20altered%20by%20the%20attacker%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20wrote%20in%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20created%20cloned%20versions%20of%20the%20Meta%20Quest%20Browser%20and%20VRChat%20app.%20Once%20the%20replica%20browser%20app%20was%20running%2C%20the%20re