ower%20eligible%20borrowers'%20closing%20costs%2C%20meaning%20they'd%20need%20less%20cash%20to%20close%20on%20the%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20announced%20the%20pilot%20at%20his%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address%2C%20where%20he%20outlined%20several%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-lower-cost-homeownership-hopeful-homebuyers-2024-3%5C%22%3Ehousing%20proposals%20aimed%20at%20making%20homeownership%20more%20affordable%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20first-time%20homebuyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20the%20FHFA's%20new%20title%20acceptance%20pilot%20works%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20FHFA's%20new%20title%20acceptance%20pilot%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FHFA%2C%20which%20oversees%20mortgage%20investors%20Fannie%20Mae%20and%20Freddie%20Mac%2C%20will%20allow%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhen-to-refinance-mortgage%5C%22%3Emortgage%20refinances%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20sold%20to%20Fannie%20or%20Freddie%20without%20requiring%20a%20lender's%20title%20insurance%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20or%20refinance%20a%20home%2C%20a%20title%20search%20is%20completed%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20unknown%20parties%20have%20a%20claim%20to%20the%20property.%20Title%20insurance%20then%20protects%20the%20policyholder%20from%20losses%20related%20to%20a%20title%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20are%20required%20to%20purchase%20a%20lender's%20title%20insurance%20policy%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20significant%20out-of-pocket%20cost.%20The%20title%20acceptance%20pilot%20waives%20this%20cost%20for%20eligible%20refinance%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20currently%20a%20temporary%20program%20that%20is%20small%20in%20scope.%20Only%20borrowers%20who%20have%20more%20than%2020%25%20equity%20in%20their%20home%20and%20live%20in%20%26quot%3Bselect%20geographies%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20eligible%2C%20says%20the%20FHFA.%20It%20will%20also%20only%20be%20available%20on%20loans%20that%20have%20been%20deemed%20to%20have%20low%20title%20risk%20based%20on%20an%20automated%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Potential%20refinance%20closing%20cost%20savings%5C%22%3EPotential%20refinance%20closing%20cost%20savings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20eligible%20for%20this%20program%2C%20how%20much%20you%20could%20save%20depends%20on%20how%20much%20a%20title%20insurance%20policy%20typically%20costs%20in%20your%20area.%20The%20average%20homeowner%20could%20save%20%24750%20on%20their%20closing%20costs%20thanks%20to%20this%20new%20program%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F03%2F07%2Ffact-sheet-president-biden-announces-plan-to-lower-housing-costs-for-working-families%2F%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20FHFA%20says%20that%20savings%20could%20range%20between%20%24300%20to%20%241%2C500.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Pushback%20from%20the%20mortgage%20industry%5C%22%3EPushback%20from%20the%20mortgage%20industry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELeaders%20from%20the%20mortgage%20and%20title%20insurance%20industries%20overall%20weren't%20pleased%20with%20this%20announcement.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alta.org%2Fnews-and-publications%2Fpress-release%2FALTA-Says-White-House-Attack-on-Title-Insurance-Offers-False-Promise-of-Savings%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Land%20Title%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bpurely%20political%20gesture%20offering%20a%20false%20promise%20of%20savings%20for%20homeowners%20while%20exposing%20consumers%2C%20lenders%2C%20and%20taxpayers%20to%20greater%20financial%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mba.org%2Fnews-and-research%2Fnewsroom%2Fnews%2F2024%2F03%2F07%2Fmba-statement-on-the-biden-administration-s-housing-affordability-initiatives-warns-against-cfpb-reforms-on-closing-costs-title-insurance%5C%22%3EMortgage%20Bankers%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bhas%20significant%20concerns%20that%20some%20of%20the%20proposals%20on%20closing%20costs%20and%20title%20insurance%20could%20undermine%20consumer%20protections%2C%20increase%20risk%2C%20and%20reduce%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20this%20pilot%20program%20could%20be%20continued%20or%20expanded%20down%20the%20road%2C%20particularly%20without%20industry%20buy-in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Closing%20costs%20remain%20a%20major%20hurdle%20for%20many%20borrowers%5C%22%3EClosing%20costs%20remain%20a%20major%20hurdle%20for%20many%20borrowers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20also%20announced%20during%20the%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumerfinance.gov%2Fabout-us%2Fblog%2Fjunk-fees-are-driving-up-housing-costs-the-cfpb-wants-to-hear-from-you%2F%5C%22%3EConsumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20ways%20to%20reduce%20closing%20costs%20for%20all%20mortgage%20borrowers%2C%20not%20just%20those%20who%20are%20refinancing.%20This%20will%20be%20especially%20beneficial%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-first-time-homebuyer-loans%5C%22%3Efirst-time%20homebuyers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20often%20have%20less%20cash%20saved%20up%20to%20bring%20to%20the%20closing%20table.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20we%20can%20save%20money%2C%20that's%20money%20that%20can%20go%20towards%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-much-down-payment-for-a-house%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Christopher%20Tyson%2C%20president%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncst.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Community%20Stabilization%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20non-profit%20whose%20mission%20is%20expanding%20affordable%20homeownership.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20money%20that%20can%20be%20saved%20and%20applied%20later%20for%20any%20type%20of%20costs%20associated%20with%20moving%20into%20a%20new%20home%20or%20other%20costs%20down%20the%20road.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20buying%20or%20refinancing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-are-mortgage-closing-costs%5C%22%3Emortgage%20closing%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20usually%20end%20up%20being%20a%20significant%20sum%2C%20typically%20ranging%20from%203%25%20to%206%25%20of%20the%20loan%20amount.%20This%20means%20that%20on%20a%20low%20down%20payment%20mortgage%2C%20like%20a%20conventional%20loan%20that%20only%20requires%203%25%20down%2C%20a%20borrower%20could%20actually%20end%20up%20paying%20more%20in%20closing%20costs%20than%20they%20will%20on%20their%20down%20payment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20looking%20at%20the%20bigger%20picture%2C%20lowering%20closing%20costs%20is%20only%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20what%20needs%20to%20happen%20to%20make%20homeownership%20more%20affordable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20greatest%20challenges%20to%20affordability%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20supply%2C%26quot%3B%20Tyson%20says.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20a%20historic%20supply%20crisis%20across%20the%20nation%20in%20many%20markets%2C%20and%20that%20is%20driving%20up%20costs%20for%20homebuyers%20and%20taking%20opportunities%20off%20the%20table%20for%20would-be%20homeowners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20qualified%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20in%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAdvisor%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%