olls%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Election%20Commission%20Confirms%20Receipt%20of%20Electoral%26nbsp%3BBonds%26nbsp%3BData%20From%20SBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04200200%2F3076973126_ab45efee1b_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20has%20furnished%20information%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20purchased%20and%20encashed%20since%202019%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpokespersonECI%2Fstatus%2F1767547904171069452%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20confirmed%20receipt%20of%20the%20data%20from%20the%20SBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20compliance%20of%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20directions%20to%20the%20SBI%2C%20contained%20in%20its%20order%20dated%20Feb%2015%20%26amp%3B%20March%2011%2C%202024%20(in%20the%20matter%20of%20WPC%20NO.880%20of%202017)%2C%20data%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20has%20been%20supplied%20by%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20today%2C%20March%2012%2C%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20post%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Felectoral-bonds-case-sc-dismisses-sbis-plea-for-extension-says-disclose-information-by-march-12%5C%22%3Erejected%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20plea%20for%20extra%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20till%20June%2030%20to%20furnish%20the%20details%20and%20asked%20it%20to%20do%20so%20by%20today%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20may%20proceed%20against%20the%20bank%20on%20grounds%20on%20wilful%20disobedience%20if%20the%20new%20deadline%20was%20not%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20asked%20the%20ECI%20to%20make%20the%20details%20public%20on%20its%20website%20by%20Friday%20(March%2015).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20by%20reporters%20to%20confirm%20when%20it%20would%20upload%20the%20details%20onto%20its%20site%2C%20the%20ECI%20did%20not%20immediately%20offer%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ELaw%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20news%20site%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLawTodayLive%2Fstatus%2F1767536659191693822%5C%22%3Ecited%20ECI%20sources%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20because%20the%20data%20is%20in%20a%20raw%20format%2C%20its%20upload%20by%20Friday%20%E2%80%9Cis%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20challenge%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectoral%20bonds%20are%20interest-free%20financial%20instruments%20that%20individuals%20or%20groups%20may%20use%20to%20make%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-electoral-bonds-quash-anonymous%5C%22%3Eon%20February%2015%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20the%20bonds%20violated%20voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20information%20and%20were%20thus%20unconstitutional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20judgement%2C%20the%20top%20court%20gave%20the%20SBI%20time%20till%20March%206%20to%20provide%20information%20to%20the%20ECI%20on%20the%20details%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20purchased%20since%20April%2012%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20data%20was%20to%20include%20the%20date%20the%20bonds%20were%20purchased%20on%2C%20their%20denominations%20and%20the%20names%20of%20who%20purchased%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20ordered%20for%20data%20on%20every%20electoral%20bond%20encashed%20by%20political%20parties%20since%20that%20date%20to%20be%20furnished%2C%20including%20the%20date%20they%20were%20encashed%20on%20and%20the%20bonds%E2%80%99%20denominations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20before%20the%20March%206%20deadline%2C%20the%20SBI%20said%20it%20needed%20time%20till%20June%2030%20to%20furnish%20the%20data%20because%20it%20had%20to%20compile%2044%2C434%20sets%20of%20information%20from%20two%20%E2%80%98information%20silos%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20asked%20the%20bank%20what%20it%20had%20done%20since%20February%2015%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20bank%20already%20had%20the%20necessary%20information%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Fbiz-tech%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2Fsbi-issues-electoral-bonds-worth-rs-16518-crore-in-30-tranches.html%5C%22%3ERs%2016%2C518%20crore%20worth%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20sold%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%202018%20to%20the%20start%20of%202024%2C%20the%20government%20recently%20informed%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%20has%20by%20far%20been%20the%20biggest%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%20number%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20%E2%80%93%20worth%20Rs%2012%2C008%20crore%20%E2%80%93%20sold%20between%202017-2018%20and%202022-2023%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20nearly%2055%25%2C%20or%20Rs%206%2C564%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710250529000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F04200200%2F3076973126_ab45efee1b_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsbi-hands-over-electoral-bonds-data-eci-no-receipt-data%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission's%20confirmation%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdata%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20has%20been%20supplied%20by%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20today%2C%20March%2012%2C%202024.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsbi-hands-over-electoral-bonds-data-eci-no-receipt-data%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98All%20of%20Us%20Strangers%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Fever%20Dream%20of%20Love%2C%20Longing%20and%20Loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12174942%2Fimage-1944.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EHave%20you%20experienced%20a%20strange%20kind%20of%20delirium%20right%20before%20waking%20up%20from%20a%20dream%3F%20Especially%20when%20a%20dream%20is%20so%20lucid%20and%20visceral%20that%20it%20feels%20real.%20There%E2%80%99s%20even%20a%20stretch%20when%20one%20is%20simultaneously%20aware%20they%E2%80%99re%20dreaming%2C%20but%20also%20immersed%20in%20it%20like%20it%E2%80%99s%20really%20happening.%20A%20majority%20of%20Andrew%20Haigh%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EAll%20Of%20Us%20Strangers%3C%2Fem%3E%20takes%20place%20in%20a%20delirium%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdam%20(Andrew%20Scott)%2C%20a%20lonely%20screenwriter%20residing%20in%20a%20ghostly%20apartment%20building%20in%20London%20where%20he%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20two%20occupants%2C%20spends%20a%20large%20part%20of%20his%20day%20gazing%20into%20a%20distance.%20He%E2%80%99s%20either%20staring%20at%20a%20blank%20word%20document%20on%20his%20laptop%20whose%20blinking%20cursor%20is%20measuring%20his%20time%20wasted%2C%20or%20mindlessly%20watching%20TV%20while%20chomping%20snacks.%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20like%20he%20has%20friends%20(not%20nearby%2C%20at%20least)%20and%20he%20looks%20accustomed%20to%20microwave%20dinners%20and%20leftovers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20solitude%20is%20threatened%20when%20his%20only%20neighbour%20Harry%20(Paul%20Mescal)%20shows%20up%20at%20the%20door%2C%20visibly%20inebriated%20and%20slightly%20on%20edge.%20He%20asks%20Adam%20how%20he%20copes%20with%20the%20silence%20of%20their%20area%2C%20without%20throwing%20himself%20off%20the%20balcony.%20When%20Harry%20invites%20himself%20in%2C%20Adam%20turns%20him%20away%20politely%2C%20almost%20instantly%20regretting%20it.%20Adam%20is%20battling%20writer%E2%80%99s%20block%2C%20and%20it%20seems%20like%20he%E2%80%99s%20also%20spent%20a%20lifetime%20running%20away%20from%20relationships.%20A%20spot%20decision%20to%20look%20at%20his%20childhood%20things%20(for%20inspiration)%20causes%20him%20to%20visit%20his%20parents%E2%80%99%20home%20in%20the%20suburbs.%20While%20walking%20around%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20he%20bumps%20into%20his%20father%20(Jamie%20Bell)%2C%20who%20invites%20him%20to%20come%20pay%20his%20mother%20(Claire%20Foy)%20a%20visit.%20What%20makes%20this%20meeting%20out%20of%20the%20ordinary%20is%20%E2%80%93%20Adam%E2%80%99s%20parents%20died%20when%20he%20was%2012.%20%E2%80%9CA%20car%20crash%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adam%20tells%20Harry%2C%20the%20writer%20in%20him%20groaning%20at%20the%20cliche.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaigh%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20an%20adaptation%20of%20a%201987%20Japanese%20novel%20by%20Taichi%20Yamada%20called%20%3Cem%3EStrangers%3C%2Fem%3E.%20As%20much%20as%20it%20traverses%20the%20supernatural%2Fmagic-realism%20path%2C%20the%20grief%20and%20longing%20here%20is%20deeply%20personal.%20Having%20missed%20out%20on%20living%20his%20teenage%20years%20with%20his%20parents%2C%20Adam%20becomes%20a%20recurring%20visitor%20at%20his%20parents%E2%80%99%20home.%20Note%20the%20obedience%20in%20Scott%E2%80%99s%20eyes%2C%20like%20he%20suddenly%20transformed%20into%20the%20shy%2C%20awkward%20adolescent%20they%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20comes%20out%20to%20them%20as%20a%20gay%20man%20%E2%80%93%20resulting%20in%20two%20exceptionally%20touching%20scenes.%20Foy%20is%20exquisite%20as%20a%20mother%20grappling%20with%20memories%20of%20unconditional%20love%20for%20Adam%E2%80%99s%2012-year-old%20version%2C%20her%20%E2%80%9880s%20mindset%20clashing%20with%20contemporary%20progressive%20values%2C%20while%20still%20concerned%20for%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20loneliness%20and%20health.%20Her%20immediate%20question%20is%20around%20a%20disease%20she%20heard%20about%20on%20TV.%20Similarly%2C%20Bell%20is%20measured%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98alpha%E2%80%99%20Dad%2C%20who%20smokes%20like%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20fashion%20statement.%20But%20who%20also%20surprises%20his%20son%20with%20his%20generosity%20and%20introspection.%20It%E2%80%99s%20almost%20like%20Adam%20is%20concocting%20his%20own%20revisionist%20version%20of%20his%20growing%20up%20years%2C%20to%20overcome%20the%20pain%20of%20growing%20up%20isolated%20%E2%80%93%20which%20probably%20played%20a%20part%20in%20making%20him%20an%20even%20more%20isolated%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20he%20reconnects%20with%20his%20parents%2C%20the%20more%20Adam%20finds%20himself%20opening%20up%20to%20Harry.%20Haigh%E2%80%99s%20film%20creates%20the%20perfect%20time%20capsule%2C%20as%20the%2080s%20music%20becomes%20more%20and%20more%20prominent%20(Pet%20Shop%20Boys%2C%20Frankie%20Goes%20to%20Hollywood)%2C%20almost%20as%20a%20way%20of%20indicating%20that%20telling%20his%20parents%20about%20his%20unspoken%20desires%2C%20might%20have%20freed%20him%20enough%20to%20profess%20being%20attracted%20to%20another%20man.%20Mescal%2C%20in%20another%20haunted%20performance%20(after%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EAftersun%3C%2Fem%3E)%20of%20a%20man%20putting%20up%20the%20confident%2C%20assertive%20act%20while%20being%20completely%20shattered%20within%2C%20is%20a%20sight%20to%20behold.%20As%20Adam%E2%80%99s%20young%20lover%2C%20Harry%20brings%20a%20recklessness%20to%20the%20dynamic%2C%20which%20the%20former%20never%20allowed%20himself.%20Haigh%20films%20the%20sex%20scenes%20between%20Adam%20and%20Harry%20with%20a%20directness%2C%20as%20they%20explore%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20bodies%20without%20the%20shame%20that%E2%80%99s%20been%20conditioned%20into%20them%20from%20a%20young%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaigh%2C%20who%20made%20the%20similarly%20devastating%20%3Cem%3E45%20Years%3C%2Fem%3E%20(his%20economy%20could%20be%20mistaken%20for%20him%20being%20distant)%2C%20brings%20his%20fleeting%20touch%20here%20too.%20He%20maintains%20the%20plot%E2%80%99s%20ambiguity%20till%20the%20end%20%E2%80%93%20is%20Adam%E2%80%99s%20writing%20assignment%20resulting%20in%20him%20visualising%20these%20hyper-real%20conversations%3F%20Is%20he%20%E2%80%98healing%E2%80%99%20through%20these%20conversations%3F%20Or%20is%20he%20losing%20his%20mind%3F%20Will%20these%20visits%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20his%20relationship%20with%20Harry%20%E2%80%93%20who%2C%20in%20one%20scene%2C%20realises%20he%20will%20have%20to%20step%20up%20as%20the%20caregiver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20of%20Us%20Strangers%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20brimming%20with%20great%20performances%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20best%20described%20as%20an%20Andrew%20Scott%20showcase.%20Best%20known%20for%20playing%20Moriarty%20in%20Benedict%20Cumberbatch%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ESherlock%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20a%20priest%20in%20Phoebe%20Waller-Bridge%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EFleabag%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20Scott%20brings%20his%20most%20pared-down%20version%20for%20the%20part%20of%20Adam.%20He%20almost%20physically%20contracts%20himself%20around%20his%20parents%2C%20and%20gets%20comfortable%20in%20his%20own%20body%20beside%20his%20lover.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20best%20example%20of%20body-language%20acting%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20in%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaigh%20knows%20exactly%20how%20to%20leverage%20the%20school-boy%20kindness%20in%20Scott%E2%80%99s%20eyes%2C%20and%20tip%20him%20over%20during%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20eerie%20scenes.%20And%20yet%2C%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20love%20and%20longing%20permeate%20through%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20100-minute%20runtime%2C%20even%20when%20it%20turns%20into%20a%20fever%20dream.%20Would%20you%20lose%20your%20mind%20to%20speak%20to%20your%20dead%20parents%20for%20a%20few%20more%20minutes%3F%20What%20does%20unconditional%20love%20really%20mean%20%E2%80%93%20would%20you%20embrace%20a%20partner%20consumed%20by%20their%20loneliness%3F%20Would%20you%20lie%20beside%20them%20and%20offer%20them%20comfort%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20little%20to%20no%20chance%20of%20this%20effort%20being%20reciprocated%3F%20%3Cem%3EAll%20of%20Us%20Strangers%3C%2Fem%3E%20marinates%20in%20these%20questions%2C%20not%20pretending%20to%20fully%20know%20the%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710250220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12174942%2Fimage-1944.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fall-of-us-strangers-a-fever-dream-of-love-longing-and-loss%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andrew%20Haigh%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20an%20adaptation%20of%20a%201987%20Japanese%20novel%20by%20Taichi%20Yamada%20called%20'Strangers'.%20As%20much%20as%20it%20traverses%20the%20supernatural%2Fmagic-realism%20path%2C%20the%20grief%20and%20longing%20here%20is%20deeply%20personal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fall-of-us-strangers-a-fever-dream-of-love-longing-and-loss%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elections%20are%20Upon%20Us%20So%20the%20Shahenshah%20and%20Shah%20Regime%20Is%20Back%20to%20Playing%20Hindu%20vs%20Muslim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175557%2FScreenshot-2024-03-12-at-5.55.44-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20a%20Rajasthan%20businessman%20who%20had%20just%20returned%20from%20a%20very%20gratifying%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(viewing)%20at%20the%20new%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20could%20be%20heard%20complaining%20that%20even%20after%20ten%20years%20of%20Modi%2C%20the%20administrative%20and%20financial%20ecosystem%20remained%20unhelpful%20to%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20business%20people%E2%80%9D%20like%20him.%20For%20good%20measure%2C%20he%20chose%20to%20add%20that%20corruption%2C%20at%20all%20levels%2C%20remained%20as%20rampant%20%E2%80%9Cas%20before.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20easy%20to%20dismiss%20the%20businessman%E2%80%99s%20sour%20assessment%20as%20unrepresentative%20and%20extremely%20personal%3B%20but%2C%20it%20is%20fair%20to%20assume%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20political%20strategists%20will%20not%20question%20the%20thumbs%20down%20either.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20makes%20the%20Modi%20cabal%20different%20from%20others%20in%20the%20political%20arena%20is%20its%20uncanny%20ability%20to%20keep%20its%20ears%20tuned%20in%20to%20rumblings%20on%20the%20bleachers.%20Unlike%20the%20hired%20guns%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Egodi%3C%2Fem%3E%20media%20and%20paid%20mouse-pushers%20in%20the%20chambers%20of%20commerce%2C%20this%20regime%20does%20not%20allow%20itself%20to%20be%20taken%20in%20by%20its%20own%20spiel.%20Massive%20disinformation%2C%20fake%20news%20and%20extravagant%20propaganda%20do%20play%20their%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20thought%20processes%2C%20but%20Modi%20knows%20the%20extent%20of%20bogusness%20of%20the%20claims%20of%20%3Cem%3Evikas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(development)%20being%20dished%20out%20for%20public%20consumption.%20He%20and%20his%20advisors%20know%20that%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20Indians%20is%20defined%20by%20misery%20and%20hopelessness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20elections%20need%20to%20be%20won%2C%20political%20power%20needs%20to%20be%20retained%20and%20augmented%20and%20the%20Leader%E2%80%99s%20quest%20for%20personal%20glory%20has%20to%20be%20satisfied.%20For%20the%20time%20being%2C%20there%20is%20something%20called%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20which%20insists%20on%20a%20protocol%20of%20fairness%20and%20transparency.%20Every%20five%20years%2C%20the%20Leader%2C%20however%20popular%20and%20divinely%20blessed%20they%20believes%20themselves%20to%20be%2C%20must%20submit%20to%20the%20simple%20test%20of%20voters%E2%80%99%20approval%2Fdisapproval.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20three%20elements%20%E2%80%93%20two%20invisible%20and%20one%20quite%20visible%20%E2%80%93%20to%20this%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20the%20formal%20institutional%20framework%2C%20presided%20over%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20the%20basic%20expectation%20in%20our%20constitutional%20democracy%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20will%20act%20as%20a%20fair%2C%20neutral%20and%20firm%20umpire%2C%20without%20allowing%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20abuse%20its%20position%20of%20incumbency%20nor%20discriminate%20against%20challengers.%20This%20is%20mostly%20an%20invisible%20process%20but%20no%20one%20would%20dispute%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20EC%E2%80%99Is%20functioning%20today%20is%20far%20from%20reassuring.%20Which%20is%20why%20the%20Opposition%20needs%20to%20exert%20itself%20to%20ensure%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fthank-you-nita-ben-for-the-jamnagar-show%5C%22%3EThank%20You%2C%20Nita%20Ben%2C%20For%20The%20Jamnagar%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20element%2C%20also%20invisible%2C%20is%20%3Cem%3Edhandlebazzi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20(organieds%20underhandedness)%20i.e.%20the%20unseen%20rigging%20at%20different%20stages%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20voters%E2%80%99%20lists%2C%20the%20use%20of%20police%20force%20to%20keep%20minorities%20from%20voting%2C%20intimidation%20in%20the%20pooling%20booth%2C%20and%20the%20extensive%20use%20of%20money%20and%20liquor%20to%20influence%20voters.%20The%20richer%20a%20political%20party%2C%20the%20better%20equipped%20it%20is%20to%20use%20underhand%20methods.%20To%20the%20extent%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20by%20far%20the%20richest%20political%20party%2C%20it%20enjoys%20a%20deadly%20advantage%20over%20its%20rivals.%20Nor%20is%20it%20averse%20to%20using%20its%20influence%20over%20Nirvachan%20Sadan%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20its%20rivals%2C%20which%20retain%20pockets%20of%20strength%2C%20remain%20handicapped%20even%20in%20these%20tactics.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20third%20element%2C%20the%20most%20visible%2C%20is%20the%20sales%20pitch%20a%20political%20party%20chooses%20to%20make%20openly%20for%20winning%20the%20electorate%E2%80%99s%20affection.%20The%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20notify%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%2C%20four%20years%20after%20parliament%20passed%20it%2C%20is%20to%20be%20seen%20and%20applauded%20as%20the%20BJP%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20undiminished%20capacity%20for%20cynicism%20and%20realism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20crowd%20deserves%20credit%20for%20prescience%20in%20recognising%20that%20despite%20all%20the%20crowing%20about%20%E2%80%9CViksit%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20third%20largest%20economy%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20voter%20is%20skeptical%3B%C2%A0%20the%20daily%20life%20of%20the%20average%20citizen%20remains%20untouched.%20Administrative%20incompetence%2C%20political%20corruption%20and%20crony%20capitalist%20excesses%20curdle%20up%20the%20ordinary%20Indian%E2%80%99s%20existence%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20BJP%20strategists%20and%20RSS%20commissars%20know%20that%20the%20voter%20is%20unimpressed%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9CModi%20Sarkar%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20notwithstanding%20the%20crores%20of%20tax-payers%E2%80%99%20money%20that%20has%20been%20spent%20on%20building%20a%20cult%20figure%20out%20of%20a%20very%20ordinary%20man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20RSS%2C%20Modi%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20gang%20are%20now%20doing%20what%20they%20have%20always%20done%20well%20%E2%80%93%20working%20the%20Hindu-Muslim%20divide.%20Slogans%20like%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Esaab%20ka%20saath%2C%20saab%20ka%20vikas%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20sounded%20good%20to%20the%20Hindu%20middle%20classes%20who%20are%20reluctant%20to%20subscribe%20to%20the%20basic%20catechism%20of%20bigotry%3B%20the%20so-called%20outreach%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9CPasmandas%E2%80%9D%20was%20heady%20stuff%20and%20conflicted%20all%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmoderate%E2%80%9D%20Muslims%20and%20confused%20many%20a%20psephologist.%20But%20the%20good%20doctor%20always%20knew%20he%20was%20administering%20a%20placebo%20%E2%80%93%20just%20as%20the%20Delhi%20police%20sub-inspector%20knew%20that%20he%20had%20a%20license%20to%20kick%20namazis%20in%20broad%20day-light.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20the%20extent%20that%20the%20CAA%20was%20designed%20and%20marketed%20as%20a%20blatantly%20anti-Muslim%20measure%2C%20its%20%E2%80%9Coperationalisation%E2%80%9D%20just%20a%20few%20days%20before%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20is%20a%20massive%20acknowledgement%20of%20inner%20doubts%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20inner%20court.%20But%20being%20the%20most%20practiced%20and%20most%20adroit%20bluff-masters%20in%20the%20public%20square%2C%20the%20Shahenshah%20and%20Shah%20duo%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20crank%20up%20visceral%20anti-Muslim%20fears%20while%20they%20tickle%20the%20collective%20Hindu%20bone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20way%20or%20the%20other%2C%20we%20are%20in%20for%20a%20season%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%20polarisation.%20While%20the%20UP%20chief%20minister%20and%20other%20lower%20order%20functionaries%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20be%20less%20restrained%20in%20their%20anti-Muslim%20rhetoric%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20use%20every%20single%20ruse%20in%20his%20voluminous%20book%20of%20tricks%20to%20foreground%20his%20Hindu-ness.%20As%20the%20latest%20Government%20of%20India%20advertisement%20(in%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20March%2012%2C%202024)%20reminds%20the%20voter%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20celebrates%20every%20Diwali%20with%20soldiers.%E2%80%9D%20Nothing%20is%20uncalculated%3B%20nothing%20is%20ever%20done%20without%20a%20long-term%20partisan%20cause%20in%20mind.%20The%20colours%20of%20the%20Parivar%20and%20contours%20of%20Bharat%20in%20his%20%E2%80%9CMera%20Bharat%2C%20Mera%20Parivar%E2%80%9D%20call%20are%20unmistakably%20tainted%20by%20the%20communal%20divide.%20Jai%20Siya%20Ram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarish%20Khare%20is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Tribune.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710249359000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175557%2FScreenshot-2024-03-12-at-5.55.44-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Felections-are-upon-us-so-the-shahenshah-and-shah-regime-is-back-to-playing-hindu-vs-muslim%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20strategists%20and%20RSS%20commissars%20know%20that%20the%20voter%20is%20unimpressed%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9CModi%20Sarkar%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20notwithstanding%20the%20crores%20of%20tax-payers%E2%80%99%20money%20that%20has%20been%20spent%20on%20building%20a%20cult%20figure%20out%20of%20a%20very%20ordinary%20man.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Felections-are-upon-us-so-the-shahenshah-and-shah-regime-is-back-to-playing-hindu-vs-muslim%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22110%20Tribal%20Artisans%20Showcased%20Lost%20Art%20Forms%20India%20Needs%20to%20Preserve%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%93%20Enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Brijesh%20Bhusara%20from%20Dadra%20Nagar%20Haveli%20walked%20the%20ramp%20at%20Samvaad.%20Back%20then%2C%20it%20was%20unusual%20for%20someone%20from%20the%20Kokna%20tribe%20to%20be%20invited%20to%20a%20fashion%20show.%20Now%2C%20nearly%20four%20years%20later%2C%20Brijesh%2C%20an%20active%20participant%20in%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%94%20Enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%20(TSF)%20%E2%80%94%20is%20celebrated%20not%20only%20by%20his%20tribe%20but%20also%20by%20neighbouring%20tribes%20like%20Konkani%2C%20Warli%2C%20and%20Dhodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20five-day%20Samvaad%20conclave%20at%20Jamshedpur%E2%80%99s%20Gopal%20Maidan%2C%20Brijesh%20and%20109%20other%20artisans%20displayed%20their%20cultural%20heritage%20through%20various%20creations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrijesh%20showcased%20traditional%20woodcrafts%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296974%2Fhow-adivasi-women-reclaim-warli-art-for-international-recognition-with-murals-gi-tags%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarli%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20giving%20a%20contemporary%20twist%20to%20a%20400-year-old%20culture.%20His%20products%20%E2%80%94%20including%20umbrellas%2C%20fridge%20magnets%2C%20shawls%2C%20saris%2C%20and%20T-shirts%20%E2%80%94%20feature%20traditional%20triangular%20figurines%20but%20use%20modern%20colour%20and%20font%20combinations.%20This%20fusion%20was%20evident%20in%20most%20stalls%20at%20the%20event%2C%20which%20transformed%20Gopal%20Maidan%20into%20a%20vibrant%20ceremonial%20ground%20with%20hand-printed%20silks%2C%20textiles%2C%20woven%20fabrics%2C%20mud%20paintings%2C%20bamboo%20items%2C%20and%20traditional%20clothing%20from%2015%20to%2019%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20Samvaad%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344526%2Fsamvaad-tata-steel-foundation-celebrates-culture-of-tribes-of-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESamvaad%2C%20enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20among%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20tribal%20gatherings%2C%20bringing%20together%20over%202%2C500%20people%20from%20200%20tribes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamvaad%2C%20which%20stepped%20into%20its%20tenth%20year%2C%20has%20created%20a%20stable%20and%20consistent%20ecosystem%20for%20dialogue%20on%20tribal%20discourse.%20Tribes%20from%20across%20India%20come%20together%20to%20address%20issues%20affecting%20their%20communities%20and%20look%20for%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20Samvaad%20has%20brought%20together%20over%2040%2C000%20people%20from%20over%20200%20tribes%20in%20India%20and%2017%20other%20countries.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010th%20edition%20commenced%20with%20the%20traditional%20beats%20of%20251%20%3Cem%3Enagadas%2C%20dhols%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20musical%20instruments%2C%20commemorating%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20the%20iconic%20tribal%20freedom%20fighter%20from%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theme%20for%20this%20edition%20was%20%E2%80%98Walk%20with%20Me%E2%80%99%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20journey%20of%20ideas%2C%20collectives%2C%20and%20changemakers%20associated%20with%20Samvaad%20since%20its%20inception.%20It%20acknowledged%20the%20impact%20of%20solution-driven%20dialogues%20and%20conversations%20from%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319311%2Fsheela-powel-helps-toda-women-sell-traditional-embroidery-shalom-ooty%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20art%20and%20craft%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20extinction%20due%20to%20several%20reasons%20like%20lack%20of%20remuneration%2C%20migration%2C%20or%20the%20next%20generation%20does%20not%20want%20to%20do%20it.%20We%20have%20been%20working%20on%20reviving%20the%20art%20by%20solving%20these%20problems.%20Art%20is%20directly%20related%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20identity%20and%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%20Smita%20Verma%2C%20Lead%20%E2%80%93%20Gender%20%26amp%3B%20Community%20Enterprise%2C%20TSF%2C%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20are%20proud%20of%20our%20identity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Brijesh%2C%20the%20Sankalp%20Foundation%20involves%20around%20300%20people%20from%2072%20villages.%20This%20collective%20provides%20a%20platform%20for%20artists%20to%20learn%20about%20current%20trends%20and%20marketing%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20beautiful%20chaos%20when%20multiple%20tribal%20communities%20come%20together%20to%20make%20the%20products.%20Although%20the%20communities%20have%20different%20traditions%2C%20their%20turmoil%20is%20mostly%20similar%2C%20which%20then%20becomes%20a%20point%20of%20unity.%20People%20that%20were%20once%20ashamed%20of%20their%20skills%20and%20identities%20are%20now%20proudly%20wearing%20and%20adorning%20them%20while%20making%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Brijesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20close%20to%20nature%2C%20the%20Sankalp%20Foundation%20is%20happy%20to%20walk%20on%20the%20sustainability%20route.%20All%20their%20wooden%20products%20are%20made%20from%20fallen%3Cem%3E%20chikoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20twigs%20and%20branches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESustainability%20is%20also%20a%20winner%20in%20Brijesh%E2%80%99s%20neighbouring%20handloom%20stall%20belonging%20to%20the%20Bodo%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331624%2Fassam-man-quits-his-job-to-make-sustainable-toys-that-represent-assams-tribes-and-culture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribes%20of%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20our%20cotton%20clothes%20are%20made%20from%20natural%20colours%20that%20last%20forever%20and%20are%20also%20good%20for%20the%20skin.%20We%20make%20colours%20from%20turmeric%2C%20leaves%20from%20plants%20and%20a%20few%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaison%20Bhramo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyotisankar%20Sahu%20of%20the%20Sabar%20tribe%20from%20Odisha%20is%20here%20for%20the%20second%20time.%20For%20him%2C%20the%20best%20benefit%20of%20putting%20up%20a%20stall%20is%20making%20his%20digital%20debut.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20group%20of%2070%20people%20who%20make%20brass%20showpieces.%20We%20always%20get%20orders%20after%20we%20return%20home%20from%20the%20conclave.%20Samvaad%20is%20a%20good%20platform%20to%20preserve%20our%20culture%20and%20tell%20the%20world%20about%20the%20exceptional%20skills%20that%20we%20learnt%20from%20our%20ancestors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20exposure%2C%20the%20artisans%20are%20also%20happy%20to%20see%20people%20taking%20an%20interest%20in%20their%20traditions.%20Sangeeta%20Meda%20from%20the%20Bhil%20tribe%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20second%20time%20here%2C%20and%20people%20always%20ask%20us%20about%20our%20history%20and%20the%20significance%20of%20our%20Bhil%20Pithora%20paintings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20ancestors%20would%20make%20these%20dotted%20paintings%20on%20walls%20during%20festivities.%20Gradually%2C%20they%20moved%20onto%20paper.%20Our%20paintings%20tell%20the%20stories%20of%20our%20origin%20and%20who%20we%20are.%20While%20selling%2C%20we%20let%20the%20customers%20know%20our%20intention%20behind%20choosing%20a%20particular%20colour%20and%20theme.%20They%20feel%20connected%20to%20us.%20My%20grandmother%2C%20Buri%20Bai%2C%20was%20awarded%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20her%20preservation%20efforts.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20carry%20forward%20her%20legacy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%20shares%20that%20the%20family%20starts%20the%20work%20nearly%20eight%20months%20before%20Samvaad%20as%20it%20takes%2010%20days%20to%20make%20one%20painting.%20She%20happily%20adds%20that%20their%20paintings%20sell%20like%20hotcakes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20stalls%20away%20is%20Dinabandhu%20Soren%20from%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Ho%20tribe.%20It%20is%20his%20ninth%20year%20at%20Samvaad%2C%20and%20each%20year%20has%20been%20fruitful%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSelling%20our%20paintings%20was%20a%20loss-making%20business%20in%20Ganjam%20district%20till%20we%20learnt%20about%20Samvaad.%20The%20workshops%20helped%20create%20a%20balance%20between%20our%20traditional%20painting%20techniques%20and%20the%20market%20demands.%20With%20a%20few%20tweaks%20and%20the%20right%20market%20linkages%2C%20we%20sold%20%3Cem%3Egond%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Esohra%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejuang%3C%2Fem%3E%20paintings%20at%20Samvaad%20and%20across%20India.%20We%20were%20even%20selected%20to%20do%20live%20sketching%20at%20G20%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20an%20art%20teacher%20at%20Srujanika%2C%20a%20women-led%20self-help%20group.%20Srujanika%20has%2030%20women%20who%20make%20paintings%2C%20Army%20uniforms%2C%20and%20other%20merchandise%20like%20%3Cem%3Edupattas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20T-shirts%20throughout%20the%20year.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20profits%2C%20the%20women%20are%20passing%20on%20the%20skills%20to%20their%20children%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYazile%20from%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Rengma%20tribe%20has%20a%20similar%20journey%2C%20from%20no%20sales%20to%20selling%20pan%20India.%20%E2%80%9CNearly%20every%20homemaker%20in%20the%20Dimapur%20area%20can%20make%20our%20traditional%20attire%2C%20%3Cem%3Emekhelas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20shawls.%20The%20skills%20were%20there%2C%20but%20the%20selling%20opportunity%20was%20missing.%20We%20attended%20a%20workshop%20at%20Samvaad%20and%20learned%20that%20new%20designs%20can%20be%20implemented%20on%20pillow%20covers%2C%20cushion%20covers%2C%20T-shirts%2C%20etc.%20In%20our%20second%20year%2C%20we%20did%20that%20and%20made%20profits.%20I%20also%20made%20friends%20from%20other%20tribal%20communities%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20fashion%20trends%20across%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yazile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20art%20and%20craft%20workshops%20helped%20artists%20like%20Yazile%20and%20Dinabandhu%20post-pandemic%20when%20the%20market%20crashed%20and%20selling%20at%20local%20%3Cem%3Ehaats%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecame%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20building%20online%20market%20links%20for%2026%20tribal%20communities%20representing%2030%20art%20forms.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3EToda%3C%2Fem%3E%20embroidery%20of%20Nilgiris%2C%20%3Cem%3EMuga%20%3C%2Fem%3Esilk%20of%20Assam%2C%20and%20more%20as%20popular%20as%20%3Cem%3EBanarasi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EIkat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EChikankari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20brought%20in%20experts%20from%20NIFT%20and%20NID%20to%20impart%20the%20skills%2C%20colour%20combinations%2C%20motifs%2C%20etc%2C%20that%20meet%20customer%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Smita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrends%20in%20the%20metro%20change%20fast%2C%20so%20we%20ask%20them%20not%20to%20change%20their%20cultural%20identity.%C2%A0%20But%20they%20can%20experiment%20with%20colours%20and%20motifs.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20pastel%20colour%20is%20in%20the%20market%2C%20infuse%20those%20colours%20in%20the%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thronging%20crowds%20at%20handicraft%20stalls%20were%20proof%20that%20the%20workshops%20were%20beneficial.%20Chaaya%20Saraiwala%2C%20an%20attendee%2C%20purchased%20Yazile%E2%80%99s%20shawls%20and%20Brijesh%E2%80%99s%20fridge%20magnets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20first%20time%20attending%20Samvaad%20and%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20see%20the%20myriad%20products%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20our%20country.%20I%20have%20bought%20a%20few%20items%20for%20my%20family.%20Each%20product%20has%20a%20story%20to%20tell.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20history%20that%20we%20do%20not%20know%2C%20but%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20conclaves%20like%20Samvaad%20are%20changing%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710249302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344574%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20Tata%20Samvaad%20conclave%20in%20Jamshedpur%2C%20artisans%20from%20indigenous%20tribes%20across%20India%20shone%20a%20spotlight%20on%20fading%20tribal%20arts%2C%20reviving%20them%20with%20contemporary%20flair%20to%20build%20livelihoods.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Gopi%20Karelia%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344574%2Ftata-samvaad-tribal-conclave-preserves-lost-heritage-artisans-sell-handicrafts%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20baby%20dies%20in%20Lanzarote%20crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710249180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-lanzarote-crash_6487998.jpg%3F20240312131659%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-baby-dies-and-family-members-injured-in-lanzarote-crash-13093210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20British%20baby%20has%20died%20after%20a%20car%20crashed%20into%20a%20group%20of%20holidaymakers%20in%20Lanzarote%2C%20according%20to%20local%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A281%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-baby-dies-and-family-members-injured-in-lanzarote-crash-13093210%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbritish-baby-dies-and-family-members-injured-in-lanzarote-crash-13093210%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbritish-baby-dies-and-family-members-injured-in-lanzarote-crash-13093210%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Astronauts%20leave%20treats%20behind%20on%20space%20station%20as%20they%20splash%20down%20after%20months%20in%20orbit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%2