Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%20(TSF)%2C%20which%20brings%20together%20the%20diverse%20tribes%20of%20India%20on%20one%20platform%20for%20a%20five-day-long%20festivity%2C%20which%20lets%20everyone%20immerse%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274494%2Fgond-artist-artwork-museums-france-usa-uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etribal%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritesh%20belongs%20to%20one%20of%20the%20200%20tribal%20communities%20participating%20in%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20tribal%20conclave%20which%20brings%20together%20tribes%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20beyond.%20It%20is%20emerging%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20platforms%20for%20dialogues%20on%20tribal%20discourse%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Performance%20at%20Samvaad%20on%20Gopal%20Maidan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-1710165483-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FGopal_Maidan_performance_11zon-171016