haracterised%20by%20struggle%2C%20and%20a%20happier%20period%20after%20he%20turned%20eight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20moving%20to%20Gurugram%2C%20Bappan%20started%20attending%20classes%20at%20the%20Nayi%20Disha%20NGO%20%E2%80%94%20started%20in%202014%20by%20Seema%20Seth%20%E2%80%94%20right%20near%20the%20slum%20cluster%20where%20he%20lived%20with%20his%20parents%20in%20Harijan%20Basti%20in%20DLF%20Phase%20V%2C%20Gurugram.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20learnt%20so%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341616%2Fbest-books-on-disability-inclusivity-mental-health-stigma-sign-language-books%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20subjects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20me%20excitedly.%20%E2%80%9CSeema%20ma%E2%80%99am%20would%20take%20us%20everywhere!%20We%20would%20play%2C%20study%2C%20and%20have%20fun.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20currently%20a%20student%20at%20the%20VIDYA%20NIOS%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20Bappan%20shares%20that%20the%20foundation%20of%20his%20educational%20pursuits%20was%20laid%20at%20Nayi%20Disha.%20From%20a%20young%20boy%20disinterested%20in%20education%20to%20now%20an%20adolescent%20who%20harbours%20dreams%20of%20becoming%20an%20engineer%20someday%2C%20Bappan%E2%80%99s%20story%20makes%20Seema%20smile%2C%20and%20watching%20him%20scale%20makes%20her%20feel%20very%20proud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20just%20one%20example%20of%20how%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340084%2Fgujarat-school-for-the-blind-and-visually-impaired-inclusive-design-architecture-by-anand-sonecha-sealabs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediligence%20can%20change%20a%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%2C%20I%20never%20imagined%20doing%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20Seema%20is%20modest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20must%20admit%20as%20she%20chronicles%20her%20journey%20from%20an%20HR%20professional%20with%2030%20years%20under%20her%20bel