20oil%20to%20women%20in%20our%20society.%20To%20our%20surprise%2C%20they%20kept%20coming%20back%20for%20more.%20In%20fact%2C%20our%20doorbell%20used%20to%20keep%20ringing%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20they%20would%20pack%20the%20oil%20in%20normal%20bottles%20with%20a%20sticker.%20The%20first%20batch%20of%20one%20litre%20was%20made%20on%20a%20small%20kadhai%20and%20sold%2010%20bottles.%20As%20soon%20as%20Nidhi%20posted%20on%20a%20Whatsapp%20group%2C%20they%20were%20sold%20out%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20925px)%20100vw%2C%20925px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22925%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi%20and%20Rajni%20started%20making%20the%20hair%20oil%20for%20their%20own%20use%20in%202020%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491.jpeg%20925w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-234x300.jpeg%20234w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-500x641.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-768x985.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhii-1709647491-150x192.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343999%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221186%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENidhi%20and%20Rajni%20started%20making%20the%20hair%20oil%20for%20their%20own%20use%20in%202020%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20they%20had%20given%20their%20oil%20to%20over%20200%20people%20in%20the%20society%2C%20the%20software%20engineer%20realised%20the%20viability%20of%20her%20business.%20As%20orders%20increased%2C%20they